Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.34,0:01:05.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Excelsior's zeal. If that annoys you, you're in the wrong lecture.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.24,0:01:12.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, this morning we're going to do it differently.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.41,0:01:14.91,Default,,0,0,0,,We always start at the end and work back to the beginning.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.36,0:01:19.92,Default,,0,0,0,,And so I thought we'd do the same thing this morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.48,0:01:26.96,Default,,0,0,0,,How many people are new? We always have to find out how many are new.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.22,0:01:28.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, my goodness. Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.64,0:01:35.34,Default,,0,0,0,,All right. So for the new people, we run through the whole presentation.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.34,0:01:38.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, for the new people, yes, we run through the whole presentation.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.58,0:01:47.05,Default,,0,0,0,,And for those that are not new, we always have something different and noteworthy.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.05,0:02:03.74,Default,,0,0,0,,And, in fact, you can't get to heaven without a few laughs, I guarantee it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.05,0:02:12.25,Default,,0,0,0,,All right. So I thought this morning we would start out.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.37,0:02:12.65,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, I'm going to start out.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.65,0:02:12.67,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, I'm going to start out.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.67,0:02:14.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm working on three books right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.07,0:02:17.79,Default,,0,0,0,,One of the books is a collection of all the slides.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.51,0:02:22.43,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll have, like, 100 slides, and then, you know, you flip the book over,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.51,0:02:25.63,Default,,0,0,0,,and then there's a page of explanation or two of explanation
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.63,0:02:29.07,Default,,0,0,0,,so that you can, like, recapitulate it like a course.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.03,0:02:35.51,Default,,0,0,0,,There's 10,000 Ways to God, and we've covered a lot of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.86,0:02:40.98,Default,,0,0,0,,We got a few left, and I got re-instructions.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.98,0:02:42.64,Default,,0,0,0,,What about the last three or four?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.64,0:02:51.17,Default,,0,0,0,,All right. So I thought this morning, yes, we'll start with the end.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.45,0:03:00.43,Default,,0,0,0,,We always tell people that one way to realize the presence of God as the source
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.43,0:03:05.91,Default,,0,0,0,,of your own existence, you know, is to constantly be in a contemplative state,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.91,0:03:06.91,Default,,0,0,0,,contemplative state.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.91,0:03:14.07,Default,,0,0,0,,And in a contemplative state, all of a sudden, out of nowhere, you witness that everything is
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.07,0:03:14.57,Default,,0,0,0,,spontaneous.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.57,0:03:19.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Spontaneously happening of its own, that nothing is being caused by anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.09,0:03:26.01,Default,,0,0,0,,That gets you out of identifying with the linear domain of content
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.01,0:03:27.91,Default,,0,0,0,,and takes you into context.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.63,0:03:34.01,Default,,0,0,0,,And you see that all is happening spontaneously of its own
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.01,0:03:41.02,Default,,0,0,0,,because what you're witnessing is evolution and creation are one and the same thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.02,0:03:46.08,Default,,0,0,0,,The universe was created, you know, is a spontaneous,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.30,0:03:53.54,Default,,0,0,0,,effulgence of divinity, which by its own nature is evolutionary, both in the linear
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.54,0:03:58.70,Default,,0,0,0,,domain we see in the physical world and in the non-linear domain.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.70,0:04:04.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Our spiritual evolution is facilitated by this world the way it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.48,0:04:10.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurrah for the world the way it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.88,0:04:20.60,Default,,0,0,0,,A lot of people don't surrender the ego and give up and experience God until you put a
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.60,0:04:22.41,Default,,0,0,0,,gun to their head.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.41,0:04:23.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Bam!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.79,0:04:31.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Therefore, demeaning guns, you see what I'm saying, you're depriving people of a pathway
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.42,0:04:44.80,Default,,0,0,0,,to God.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.80,0:04:51.06,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no point in moaning about the way the world is because everything is perfect
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.06,0:04:53.06,Default,,0,0,0,,for our own spiritual evolution.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.06,0:04:58.94,Default,,0,0,0,,When you stop thinking of the world critically, then you see it's perfect just the way it
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.94,0:04:59.94,Default,,0,0,0,,is.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.94,0:05:01.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Maximum karmic opportunity.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.44,0:05:03.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Undue negative karma.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.32,0:05:03.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Gain.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.84,0:05:06.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Maintain positive karma.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.30,0:05:10.96,Default,,0,0,0,,At every instant, then, this world is perfect.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.96,0:05:14.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Agreed?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.98,0:05:15.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.98,0:05:23.60,Default,,0,0,0,,There are 10,000 ways to God, and we'll get into them next year.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.60,0:05:28.75,Default,,0,0,0,,We've gotten quite a few hundred done already.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.75,0:05:32.15,Default,,0,0,0,,So I thought we'll start with the last slide.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.15,0:05:34.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Have we got a last slide?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.46,0:05:35.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yes, we do.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.63,0:05:39.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, that's today's lecture.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.09,0:05:44.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I never know what today's lecture is until I see it on the screen.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.56,0:05:46.80,Default,,0,0,0,,People say, what are you talking about today?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.80,0:05:48.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I say, I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.96,0:05:50.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know until I get here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.66,0:05:51.92,Default,,0,0,0,,But people don't like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.92,0:05:54.86,Default,,0,0,0,,They want you to have a label for it, see?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.86,0:05:56.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.25,0:05:59.59,Default,,0,0,0,,The girls in the office say, people call and say, well, what's the lecture about?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.59,0:06:01.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, what do you think it's about?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.59,0:06:02.59,Default,,0,0,0,,It's about everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.59,0:06:03.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.59,0:06:04.59,Default,,0,0,0,,.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.59,0:06:05.59,Default,,0,0,0,,We have to make up something for them to understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.59,0:06:11.67,Default,,0,0,0,,We have to make up something for them to be happy so they sleep, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.67,0:06:16.35,Default,,0,0,0,,You notice when you pass churches, they always have Reverend Soso speaking Sunday on, and
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.35,0:06:17.83,Default,,0,0,0,,then he's probably making it up.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.83,0:06:19.49,Default,,0,0,0,,They'll say, I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.49,0:06:22.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Put anything up there that looks good.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.63,0:06:23.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Faith and prayer.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.63,0:06:24.63,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a good one.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.63,0:06:26.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Faith and prayer.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.63,0:06:29.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.86,0:06:34.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Because every point in life is an avenue to God.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.40,0:06:36.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Every single point at every instant.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.28,0:06:40.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Every little moment is an absolute doorway.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.30,0:06:44.29,Default,,0,0,0,,But today we are talking about spiritual fiction and myths.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.29,0:06:47.93,Default,,0,0,0,,We tried to be timely as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.93,0:06:53.54,Default,,0,0,0,,We live in a world and we don't want to disparage the world but see what's going on and of course
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.54,0:06:56.50,Default,,0,0,0,,right now spiritual fiction is selling very big.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.50,0:07:05.88,Default,,0,0,0,,The only trouble is, a good part of the population doesn't realize that's fiction.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.88,0:07:06.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's see.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.94,0:07:07.97,Default,,0,0,0,,.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.97,0:07:09.57,Default,,0,0,0,,this kind of stuff up here,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.03,0:07:12.13,Default,,0,0,0,,we can ask
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.13,0:07:13.53,Default,,0,0,0,,about the percent of the population.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.84,0:07:16.22,Default,,0,0,0,,More than 20%
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.22,0:07:18.24,Default,,0,0,0,,think it's real. More than
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.24,0:07:21.48,Default,,0,0,0,,40%. 42%.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.48,0:07:22.88,Default,,0,0,0,,43%.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.88,0:07:25.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright, so 42% of people
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.06,0:07:26.26,Default,,0,0,0,,believe that this fiction,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.86,0:07:28.72,Default,,0,0,0,,spiritual fiction, is real. Real.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.03,0:07:31.45,Default,,0,0,0,,So I thought, just for the
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.45,0:07:32.37,Default,,0,0,0,,record, we should
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.37,0:07:35.82,Default,,0,0,0,,give it our imprimatur.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.50,0:07:38.38,Default,,0,0,0,,You know what
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.38,0:07:40.44,Default,,0,0,0,,the imprimatur is? The Catholic Church did
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.44,0:07:42.16,Default,,0,0,0,,it for many centuries.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.80,0:07:44.64,Default,,0,0,0,,And with good
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.64,0:07:46.24,Default,,0,0,0,,cause, the Church,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.68,0:07:48.60,Default,,0,0,0,,in a sort of paternalistic fashion,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.52,0:07:51.60,Default,,0,0,0,,read all books.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.74,0:07:53.78,Default,,0,0,0,,And an imprimatur, you didn't read a book unless
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.78,0:07:55.86,Default,,0,0,0,,it had an imprimatur, means that
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.86,0:07:57.22,Default,,0,0,0,,it was read and approved.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.46,0:07:59.02,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not leading to heresy
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.02,0:08:02.06,Default,,0,0,0,,or degeneracy or immorality,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.26,0:08:02.48,Default,,0,0,0,,etc.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.06,0:08:06.08,Default,,0,0,0,,The intention of that is 375.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.46,0:08:07.72,Default,,0,0,0,,The intention is
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.72,0:08:09.96,Default,,0,0,0,,integris, to protect
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.96,0:08:12.02,Default,,0,0,0,,the innocent from being
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.02,0:08:13.98,Default,,0,0,0,,seduced by this kind of thing,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.06,0:08:16.28,Default,,0,0,0,,which in today's world is almost impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.06,0:08:18.02,Default,,0,0,0,,So I don't know if
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.02,0:08:19.78,Default,,0,0,0,,they even do it anymore, because
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.78,0:08:22.12,Default,,0,0,0,,the television and the media
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.12,0:08:23.86,Default,,0,0,0,,is so powerful.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.34,0:08:27.09,Default,,0,0,0,,But in the
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.09,0:08:29.27,Default,,0,0,0,,old days, and if a book was disapproved,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.33,0:08:30.97,Default,,0,0,0,,it was placed in the index in the
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.97,0:08:32.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Vatican. And the Vatican
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.93,0:08:35.09,Default,,0,0,0,,has thousands of volumes of books
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.09,0:08:36.55,Default,,0,0,0,,that are condemned to be heretical.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.65,0:08:39.81,Default,,0,0,0,,In today's
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.81,0:08:41.31,Default,,0,0,0,,world of libertarianism,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.47,0:08:43.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess that would sound
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.59,0:08:45.36,Default,,0,0,0,,repressive. However,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.66,0:08:47.22,Default,,0,0,0,,the intention is 375,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.58,0:08:48.82,Default,,0,0,0,,so it's an integris intention.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.60,0:08:51.58,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just paternalistic, in which
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.58,0:08:53.34,Default,,0,0,0,,the church takes some responsibility
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.34,0:08:55.10,Default,,0,0,0,,for the evolution of your soul
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.10,0:08:56.96,Default,,0,0,0,,and tries to be
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.96,0:08:58.66,Default,,0,0,0,,an adequate parent.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.32,0:09:00.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.92,0:09:03.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Spiritual fiction and myths.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.38,0:09:06.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Many of these
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.30,0:09:08.64,Default,,0,0,0,,we've spoken about before in various
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.64,0:09:10.46,Default,,0,0,0,,different ways, and I think there may be
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.46,0:09:11.68,Default,,0,0,0,,in truth versus falsehood.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.52,0:09:13.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Alien abduction.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.12,0:09:16.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Alien abduction, you know,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.80,0:09:17.64,Default,,0,0,0,,has a big press.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.24,0:09:21.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Alien abduction is a little complicated.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.30,0:09:23.38,Default,,0,0,0,,In fact, I don't know anybody
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.38,0:09:24.54,Default,,0,0,0,,that's really understood it yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.86,0:09:27.36,Default,,0,0,0,,People that visit other
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.36,0:09:29.62,Default,,0,0,0,,domains, other than our own domain,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.58,0:09:31.42,Default,,0,0,0,,do so
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.42,0:09:33.16,Default,,0,0,0,,very often in their astral body.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.92,0:09:34.62,Default,,0,0,0,,So people,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.36,0:09:37.48,Default,,0,0,0,,and I knew one in Sedona, very, very convincing,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.86,0:09:39.84,Default,,0,0,0,,visit another
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.84,0:09:40.96,Default,,0,0,0,,domain, and of course,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.99,0:09:43.77,Default,,0,0,0,,revelations in the New Testament,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.87,0:09:45.39,Default,,0,0,0,,is another domain.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.77,0:09:47.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Way down in
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.83,0:09:49.19,Default,,0,0,0,,number 70 or something.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.72,0:09:52.06,Default,,0,0,0,,What happens is
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.06,0:09:55.06,Default,,0,0,0,,the psychic body,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.16,0:09:56.48,Default,,0,0,0,,the spiritual body, I'm not using
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.48,0:09:58.00,Default,,0,0,0,,thinking of the right term, the third body,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.78,0:10:00.56,Default,,0,0,0,,leaves the physical body and
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.56,0:10:02.72,Default,,0,0,0,,visits other domains at the
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.72,0:10:04.80,Default,,0,0,0,,appeal of other
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.80,0:10:05.72,Default,,0,0,0,,entities, etc.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.41,0:10:08.65,Default,,0,0,0,,So what the person, the reason
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.65,0:10:10.65,Default,,0,0,0,,people who've been abducted are so
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.65,0:10:12.69,Default,,0,0,0,,convincing is because that's what they
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.69,0:10:13.89,Default,,0,0,0,,did experience.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.67,0:10:16.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Not in this dimension, not
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.59,0:10:18.79,Default,,0,0,0,,in physical body, but
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.79,0:10:20.79,Default,,0,0,0,,like a dream, but you're awake
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.79,0:10:22.65,Default,,0,0,0,,during the dream, they went there
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.65,0:10:24.07,Default,,0,0,0,,and literally experienced that.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.65,0:10:27.71,Default,,0,0,0,,And there was a spiritual teacher here in Sedona
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.71,0:10:29.19,Default,,0,0,0,,who brought a lot of people out here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.98,0:10:32.44,Default,,0,0,0,,The purpose was he had visited
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.44,0:10:33.26,Default,,0,0,0,,that domain.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.17,0:10:36.61,Default,,0,0,0,,But alien abduction,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.89,0:10:38.92,Default,,0,0,0,,so because
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.92,0:10:40.54,Default,,0,0,0,,you have a
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.54,0:10:42.86,Default,,0,0,0,,subjective experience of it,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.90,0:10:43.68,Default,,0,0,0,,it's very real.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.51,0:10:46.87,Default,,0,0,0,,The only thing that you realize is that it's
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.87,0:10:48.83,Default,,0,0,0,,not the same domain as
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.83,0:10:49.37,Default,,0,0,0,,this domain.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.90,0:10:53.46,Default,,0,0,0,,A million little pieces,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.64,0:10:54.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know what that is.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.03,0:10:57.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, oh, these are best-selling
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.51,0:10:59.59,Default,,0,0,0,,books. I guess that was on Oprah's
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.59,0:11:00.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Winfrey's, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.83,0:11:03.65,Default,,0,0,0,,In which there's fiction put in
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.65,0:11:04.23,Default,,0,0,0,,with fact.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.26,0:11:08.24,Default,,0,0,0,,All apocalyptic prophecies
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.24,0:11:10.00,Default,,0,0,0,,are
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.00,0:11:10.58,Default,,0,0,0,,fallacious.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.40,0:11:14.48,Default,,0,0,0,,If you've heard what the lectures said,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.44,0:11:18.72,Default,,0,0,0,,life is evolutionary
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.72,0:11:20.60,Default,,0,0,0,,and
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.96,0:11:22.84,Default,,0,0,0,,the evolution is dependent on
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.84,0:11:25.96,Default,,0,0,0,,agreements of the
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.96,0:11:27.74,Default,,0,0,0,,will, individually and collectively.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.98,0:11:29.66,Default,,0,0,0,,So therefore,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.14,0:11:31.96,Default,,0,0,0,,the future is not knowable
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.96,0:11:33.68,Default,,0,0,0,,because it hasn't been created yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.80,0:11:35.74,Default,,0,0,0,,How can you go ahead to that which is uncreated
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.74,0:11:36.82,Default,,0,0,0,,and make a prophecy?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.26,0:11:41.30,Default,,0,0,0,,The world, until I make up what I'm going to have for breakfast,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.00,0:11:43.48,Default,,0,0,0,,is not going to be the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.56,0:11:44.98,Default,,0,0,0,,You understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.27,0:11:48.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Because we ourselves,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.91,0:11:50.45,Default,,0,0,0,,by our own spiritual decisions,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.45,0:11:50.75,Default,,0,0,0,,are
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.75,0:11:54.84,Default,,0,0,0,,deciding what the future
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.84,0:11:54.94,Default,,0,0,0,,will be.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.06,0:11:58.22,Default,,0,0,0,,All apocalyptic
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.22,0:11:59.20,Default,,0,0,0,,prophecies
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.20,0:12:01.81,Default,,0,0,0,,are false.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.41,0:12:03.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Resist.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.45,0:12:05.51,Default,,0,0,0,,We have permission to resist.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.16,0:12:07.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.28,0:12:16.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Just once more, David,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.68,0:12:17.52,Default,,0,0,0,,you're going to get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.44,0:12:21.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I have a thing in my ear that goes right to God.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.15,0:12:26.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Get preachers, get on TV.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.75,0:12:28.11,Default,,0,0,0,,God told me this morning that
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.11,0:12:30.53,Default,,0,0,0,,and you notice he's got a little
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.53,0:12:31.33,Default,,0,0,0,,thing in his ear.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.95,0:12:36.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Apocalyptic prophecies.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.82,0:12:38.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Aquarian cults.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.14,0:12:40.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Aquarian cults.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.40,0:12:43.80,Default,,0,0,0,,All these conspiracy theories.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.18,0:12:45.06,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, behind everything
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.06,0:12:46.36,Default,,0,0,0,,there's a conspiracy theory.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.92,0:12:49.22,Default,,0,0,0,,And a lot of these, of course, are just conspiracy theories.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.15,0:12:53.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Most conspiracy theories, of course,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.47,0:12:53.95,Default,,0,0,0,,are just
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.95,0:12:56.83,Default,,0,0,0,,projections of your own imagination.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.87,0:12:59.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Area 51, we've checked it out
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.53,0:13:00.37,Default,,0,0,0,,many times
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.37,0:13:02.55,Default,,0,0,0,,and there's nothing going on.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.81,0:13:06.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll tell you the truth
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.31,0:13:07.55,Default,,0,0,0,,about Area 51.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.55,0:13:09.80,Default,,0,0,0,,You won't tell anybody, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.52,0:13:13.66,Default,,0,0,0,,It's boring and there's nothing going on there.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.08,0:13:18.02,Default,,0,0,0,,The local tourist
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.02,0:13:20.22,Default,,0,0,0,,information bureau
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.22,0:13:21.64,Default,,0,0,0,,is not happy with that, but it's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.09,0:13:25.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Astrological religions.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.15,0:13:25.97,Default,,0,0,0,,See?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.61,0:13:28.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Because you're getting cause and effect
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.39,0:13:31.69,Default,,0,0,0,,and the dimensions are all mixed up.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.42,0:13:34.54,Default,,0,0,0,,The planets exist
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.54,0:13:36.90,Default,,0,0,0,,in a physical dimension.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.51,0:13:39.11,Default,,0,0,0,,They are
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.11,0:13:40.21,Default,,0,0,0,,three-dimensional.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.03,0:13:42.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.02,0:13:45.96,Default,,0,0,0,,The truth of what you are spiritually
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.96,0:13:47.94,Default,,0,0,0,,is non-linear.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.04,0:13:52.14,Default,,0,0,0,,So what astrological religions are saying
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.14,0:13:53.50,Default,,0,0,0,,is that the linear
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.50,0:13:56.40,Default,,0,0,0,,has dominion over the non-linear.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.07,0:13:59.01,Default,,0,0,0,,No such thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.86,0:14:02.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Planetary system is content.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.38,0:14:05.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Divinity, spirituality,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.34,0:14:07.74,Default,,0,0,0,,consciousness, the spirit
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.74,0:14:08.90,Default,,0,0,0,,is non-linear.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.92,0:14:11.66,Default,,0,0,0,,The non-linear is not subject
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.66,0:14:12.60,Default,,0,0,0,,to the linear.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.76,0:14:15.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Much less by causality.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.26,0:14:17.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Much less by causality.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.47,0:14:21.01,Default,,0,0,0,,So if Mercury is going over
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.01,0:14:22.49,Default,,0,0,0,,your outhouse tomorrow morning,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.61,0:14:28.07,Default,,0,0,0,,it doesn't mean your mother-in-law
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.07,0:14:29.17,Default,,0,0,0,,is going to have a heart attack.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.31,0:14:29.73,Default,,0,0,0,,You know what I'm saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.29,0:14:39.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Because all exists in one universe, however,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.43,0:14:42.09,Default,,0,0,0,,there is sometimes a correlation,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.39,0:14:44.11,Default,,0,0,0,,but not a causal one.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.70,0:14:46.28,Default,,0,0,0,,The most propitious moment
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.28,0:14:47.86,Default,,0,0,0,,for certain things is because
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.86,0:14:50.54,Default,,0,0,0,,the context and the content
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.54,0:14:51.86,Default,,0,0,0,,tend to be in agreement,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.30,0:14:53.56,Default,,0,0,0,,but not causally.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.80,0:14:54.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Not causally.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.90,0:14:55.52,Default,,0,0,0,,You understand what I'm saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.39,0:14:59.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Mercury isn't going to poison your bathtub.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.43,0:15:00.07,Default,,0,0,0,,You know?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.78,0:15:02.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Babaji,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.72,0:15:05.22,Default,,0,0,0,,is an old myth I heard about Babaji
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.22,0:15:06.56,Default,,0,0,0,,when I first got into spiritual
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.56,0:15:08.26,Default,,0,0,0,,ooh, ah, ooh, ah, ooh.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.74,0:15:11.52,Default,,0,0,0,,He's 4,000 years old.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.60,0:15:12.80,Default,,0,0,0,,He lives in the Himalayas.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.02,0:15:13.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Right, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.70,0:15:20.51,Default,,0,0,0,,The Bible code.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.87,0:15:21.71,Default,,0,0,0,,All codes,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.47,0:15:24.29,Default,,0,0,0,,all spiritual codes are fallacious.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.72,0:15:26.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't care.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.94,0:15:29.54,Default,,0,0,0,,The number of hairs on a camel's nose.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.02,0:15:32.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I have permission to ask this.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.55,0:15:35.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I just stated it as true.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.59,0:15:37.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, correct.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.38,0:15:41.52,Default,,0,0,0,,You can see that just by knowing it
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.52,0:15:42.14,Default,,0,0,0,,with your own self.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.76,0:15:44.74,Default,,0,0,0,,All supposed secret codes,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.84,0:15:46.48,Default,,0,0,0,,secret codes in the DNA
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.48,0:15:48.54,Default,,0,0,0,,and in the germs and in microbes.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.06,0:15:51.99,Default,,0,0,0,,The book of Revelation we know about quite well.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.71,0:15:53.65,Default,,0,0,0,,And of course this is,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.41,0:15:57.61,Default,,0,0,0,,affirms that apocalyptic prophecies
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.61,0:16:00.65,Default,,0,0,0,,and celestine prophecies,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.51,0:16:03.57,Default,,0,0,0,,channeling we've already spoken about,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.67,0:16:04.57,Default,,0,0,0,,it's a limitation.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.33,0:16:08.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Crop circles turned out to be also fallacious.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.76,0:16:13.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Then we have imaginary things like crystal children, etc.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.20,0:16:15.72,Default,,0,0,0,,The Da Vinci Code
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.72,0:16:17.68,Default,,0,0,0,,and Da Vinci Code decoded.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.42,0:16:22.44,Default,,0,0,0,,How about the decoding of the decoded code of the decoded?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.66,0:16:25.46,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just as dumb as the Da Vinci Code.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.56,0:16:30.50,Default,,0,0,0,,As we said about prophecies about the future,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.66,0:16:31.98,Default,,0,0,0,,disappearance of the universe
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.98,0:16:33.90,Default,,0,0,0,,is an impossibility.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.22,0:16:37.04,Default,,0,0,0,,That would be something that's becoming nothingness.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.23,0:16:41.53,Default,,0,0,0,,The idea is that the universe is an illusion.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.97,0:16:43.47,Default,,0,0,0,,And that's an illusion,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.61,0:16:44.93,Default,,0,0,0,,that the universe is an illusion.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.52,0:16:48.42,Default,,0,0,0,,How you perceive it, of course,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.50,0:16:49.18,Default,,0,0,0,,is a projection.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.16,0:16:51.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Perception is projection.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.53,0:16:55.75,Default,,0,0,0,,All forms of divination, etc.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.35,0:16:58.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Then here we have the DNA code.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.01,0:17:00.65,Default,,0,0,0,,The end time prophecies.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.30,0:17:04.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Extraterrestrials and ghosts.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.99,0:17:05.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Everybody agree with that?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.17,0:17:07.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Anybody believe in ghosts?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.59,0:17:10.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't believe in ghosts.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.35,0:17:11.43,Default,,0,0,0,,My mother didn't believe in ghosts.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.87,0:17:13.85,Default,,0,0,0,,One time I went to school in kindergarten,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.85,0:17:14.85,Default,,0,0,0,,and there's some place around there,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.85,0:17:16.31,Default,,0,0,0,,and a kid starts telling me about ghosts.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.31,0:17:18.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I got scared of ghosts.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.01,0:17:22.47,Default,,0,0,0,,So my mother took me by the hand,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.55,0:17:23.89,Default,,0,0,0,,and we searched the house for ghosts.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.74,0:17:27.64,Default,,0,0,0,,We went in the basement,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.86,0:17:29.06,Default,,0,0,0,,we opened the closets.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.45,0:17:34.99,Default,,0,0,0,,So caringness, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.59,0:17:37.97,Default,,0,0,0,,By caringness, we eliminate the fear.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.11,0:17:38.89,Default,,0,0,0,,The fear of ghosts.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.11,0:17:42.49,Default,,0,0,0,,See, man has a certain fascination
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.49,0:17:43.77,Default,,0,0,0,,with all these illusions.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.19,0:17:46.01,Default,,0,0,0,,The romance and excitement of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.01,0:17:48.25,Default,,0,0,0,,What could be more exciting than all this stuff here?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.33,0:17:48.83,Default,,0,0,0,,You know what I'm saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.94,0:17:51.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Incoming fifth dimensions.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.66,0:17:53.32,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the future, etc.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.72,0:17:58.78,Default,,0,0,0,,The Judas Gospel, as we calibrated 170 or something.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.08,0:18:00.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Maitreya is another thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.90,0:18:01.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Another thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.60,0:18:03.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Maitreya is always showing up, much like Babaji.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.10,0:18:07.14,Default,,0,0,0,,And you read it on the internet.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.38,0:18:11.10,Default,,0,0,0,,They spotted Maitreya in a coffee shop in Chicago.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.22,0:18:16.92,Default,,0,0,0,,The return of the Christ is having a cheeseburger.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.42,0:18:21.52,Default,,0,0,0,,No, he's really spotted it all over the place.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.67,0:18:24.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Mayan calendar predictions.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.29,0:18:27.21,Default,,0,0,0,,And people are always sending me something
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.21,0:18:28.53,Default,,0,0,0,,about the Mayan calendars.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.11,0:18:31.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't like the Mayan calendars.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.26,0:18:32.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I think they're horrid.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.16,0:18:33.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't send me any more.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.98,0:18:38.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I got piles of books about Mayan calendar prophecies.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.49,0:18:42.35,Default,,0,0,0,,All prophecies about the future are impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.40,0:18:43.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.40,0:18:47.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Because that which is contributory,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.62,0:18:49.98,Default,,0,0,0,,not causal, but contributory to the future,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.08,0:18:50.52,Default,,0,0,0,,has no future.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.52,0:18:51.52,Default,,0,0,0,,It hasn't even happened yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.98,0:18:53.48,Default,,0,0,0,,So how can you know the future?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.80,0:18:54.18,Default,,0,0,0,,You understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.53,0:18:57.95,Default,,0,0,0,,If you shoot billiards, if you shoot pool, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.51,0:19:01.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Not until the pool ball hits and reverberates
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.19,0:19:02.75,Default,,0,0,0,,do you know what the future is going to be.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.81,0:19:04.17,Default,,0,0,0,,The next ball is going to be hitting.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.33,0:19:04.71,Default,,0,0,0,,You understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.74,0:19:09.18,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't skip it in pool.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.10,0:19:11.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Or, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.10,0:19:15.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Natural healing.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.02,0:19:18.14,Default,,0,0,0,,There's a book out there that is just absolutely,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.38,0:19:20.34,Default,,0,0,0,,oh, I know why I put these things on there.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.70,0:19:22.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Because they're big sellers.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.24,0:19:23.38,Default,,0,0,0,,People are impressed.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.40,0:19:26.86,Default,,0,0,0,,If it's popular, I think this was the number one book for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.60,0:19:29.24,Default,,0,0,0,,And Da Vinci was number one.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.16,0:19:31.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Celestine Prophecy was number one.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.81,0:19:35.39,Default,,0,0,0,,People think, well, if everybody agrees with it,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.43,0:19:38.03,Default,,0,0,0,,and if everybody's buying it, it must be something I'm missing.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.85,0:19:42.93,Default,,0,0,0,,So popularity is no indication of truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.58,0:19:47.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Natural healing book.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.94,0:19:51.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Negative prayer healing study was in the Journal of Cardiology,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.24,0:19:54.70,Default,,0,0,0,,and I don't know if I mentioned it last time or not,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.20,0:19:56.94,Default,,0,0,0,,was, I forget what issue, April.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.08,0:19:57.48,Default,,0,0,0,,April or something.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.36,0:19:59.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway, it got big headlines.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.10,0:20:03.56,Default,,0,0,0,,It was supported by the Templeton Foundation at over a million dollars.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.80,0:20:08.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Prayer, you know, healing and prayer studies have been done for a long, long time.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.46,0:20:11.40,Default,,0,0,0,,And the Institute of Noetic Science, I think,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.48,0:20:15.28,Default,,0,0,0,,has a whole department of it listing hundreds and hundreds of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.34,0:20:20.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Therefore, how can a negative prayer healing,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.72,0:20:24.12,Default,,0,0,0,,it should have been neutral, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.12,0:20:24.80,Default,,0,0,0,,No, it was negative.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.26,0:20:26.84,Default,,0,0,0,,It showed that it was of no use.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.08,0:20:27.46,Default,,0,0,0,,No use.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.58,0:20:33.30,Default,,0,0,0,,That's contrary to 50 years of clinical experience of my own self.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.37,0:20:39.69,Default,,0,0,0,,So if prayer and spiritual contextualization did not affect healing,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.54,0:20:44.20,Default,,0,0,0,,then the millions of people who have recovered in Alcoholics Anonymous
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.20,0:20:45.28,Default,,0,0,0,,would not have recovered.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.44,0:20:45.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.58,0:20:49.60,Default,,0,0,0,,So the clinical evidence is all these millions of people
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.60,0:20:51.34,Default,,0,0,0,,had a hopeless progressive disease,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.52,0:20:53.86,Default,,0,0,0,,which condemns you to insanity.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.86,0:20:59.02,Default,,0,0,0,,And before AA appeared, everybody died of alcoholism with wet brain,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.02,0:21:01.56,Default,,0,0,0,,and dementia, and convulsions.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.58,0:21:05.66,Default,,0,0,0,,And now the recovery rate is extraordinary, millions.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.34,0:21:10.12,Default,,0,0,0,,So if prayer and spiritual intention had no effect,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.78,0:21:12.86,Default,,0,0,0,,how did all those millions of people recover?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.42,0:21:14.40,Default,,0,0,0,,How did they recover?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.62,0:21:15.62,Default,,0,0,0,,And how do you account for that?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.46,0:21:18.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, science, which is in the 400s,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.94,0:21:21.16,Default,,0,0,0,,doesn't consider spirituality a reality.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.78,0:21:26.11,Default,,0,0,0,,So when they do their statistics, they don't even put it in.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.11,0:21:29.01,Default,,0,0,0,,And I was reading recovery groups in alcohol the other day,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.31,0:21:29.95,Default,,0,0,0,,the Psychiatric Journal,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.71,0:21:35.25,Default,,0,0,0,,and it says, and they're also advised to seek spiritual counseling.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.01,0:21:38.01,Default,,0,0,0,,But then they don't divide up the groups
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.01,0:21:39.81,Default,,0,0,0,,based on whether they did or did not,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.91,0:21:44.13,Default,,0,0,0,,because we know the recovery rate is extremely high in those who do,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.31,0:21:45.95,Default,,0,0,0,,and it's zero in those who do not.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.92,0:21:50.02,Default,,0,0,0,,So when we calibrated this million-dollar study,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.02,0:21:52.86,Default,,0,0,0,,you know, the Templeton Foundation itself is quite integrous,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.98,0:21:53.72,Default,,0,0,0,,calibrates it 500.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.99,0:21:59.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's just recalibrate that cardiology study.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.37,0:22:02.75,Default,,0,0,0,,We have permission to recalibrate it.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.23,0:22:05.41,Default,,0,0,0,,It's over 190, 195.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.70,0:22:07.40,Default,,0,0,0,,It's at 190.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.02,0:22:10.74,Default,,0,0,0,,It's supposed to be a scientific million-dollar study.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.18,0:22:12.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Calibrates it 190.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.32,0:22:16.52,Default,,0,0,0,,It means it's non-integrous by design, plus by execution.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.58,0:22:20.06,Default,,0,0,0,,And what it means to me is people who are atheistic
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.06,0:22:21.76,Default,,0,0,0,,and really hate to give any credit to God
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.76,0:22:24.94,Default,,0,0,0,,made sure that the statistics would come out supporting their position.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.04,0:22:30.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Templeton, you know, was very much into spirituality,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.14,0:22:33.24,Default,,0,0,0,,frankly got screwed out of $1 million.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.57,0:22:37.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I could have saved him a million.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.94,0:22:39.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Send it to Dave.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.83,0:22:44.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Susan will give you an answer in two seconds.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.71,0:22:47.75,Default,,0,0,0,,This project is worth investing in.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.81,0:22:48.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Her arm goes weak.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.69,0:22:50.07,Default,,0,0,0,,You just saved a million dollars.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.23,0:22:52.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, you don't have to go through the whole loss.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.32,0:23:02.70,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, so false opus, the negative prayer healing study.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.70,0:23:04.40,Default,,0,0,0,,It was the Journal of Cardiology.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.40,0:23:05.08,Default,,0,0,0,,It was April.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.26,0:23:06.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I think, or so.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.88,0:23:11.64,Default,,0,0,0,,New Ageism itself is, say, like a circus.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.64,0:23:17.18,Default,,0,0,0,,And it's full of all kinds of attractive byways,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.18,0:23:19.60,Default,,0,0,0,,most of many of them occult.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.60,0:23:22.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Quite a few of them, frankly, quite dangerous to fool with.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.38,0:23:25.05,Default,,0,0,0,,People think, oh, this is innocent.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.05,0:23:29.15,Default,,0,0,0,,And, you know, famously, Ouija boards and other forms of divination
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.15,0:23:32.63,Default,,0,0,0,,and all kinds of tarot card readings, et cetera,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.63,0:23:34.63,Default,,0,0,0,,they all calibrate below 200.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.63,0:23:40.21,Default,,0,0,0,,And if you ask, is this OK for me to go into, you will always get a no.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.21,0:23:43.51,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll always get advised to leave it alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.51,0:23:45.71,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, during one's spiritual adolescent, naturally,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.71,0:23:50.25,Default,,0,0,0,,you've got to check out everything and go to the nearest New Age fair, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.25,0:23:51.63,Default,,0,0,0,,And, of course, it is a fair.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.63,0:23:56.09,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, you go past all the booze and all the pitchmen
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.09,0:23:59.44,Default,,0,0,0,,and all the beautiful rotating figures.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.44,0:24:02.24,Default,,0,0,0,,And it's always mind-dazzling, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.24,0:24:03.84,Default,,0,0,0,,The magic healing balls.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.92,0:24:10.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Now they have them electronic.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.56,0:24:19.59,Default,,0,0,0,,The magic healing rays, $42.95, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.59,0:24:22.29,Default,,0,0,0,,OK, people check it out for the fun of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.29,0:24:23.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Opus Dei code.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.29,0:24:26.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Again, you see the word code is, again, false.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.97,0:24:31.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Protocol of the Elders of Zion I put in because falsity
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.78,0:24:35.86,Default,,0,0,0,,has such a profound effect.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:35.86,0:24:36.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I had the snake pit.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.86,0:24:39.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I still have it.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:39.38,0:24:40.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Things that are false.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:41.00,0:24:44.71,Default,,0,0,0,,People say, oh, you know, so it's not right.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:44.71,0:24:45.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Have a profound effect.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:45.95,0:24:50.93,Default,,0,0,0,,The whole Nazi era, of course, the whole Nazi era,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:50.93,0:24:55.17,Default,,0,0,0,,was energized by the energy, the protocol of the Elders of Zion,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:55.17,0:24:59.72,Default,,0,0,0,,which I think calibrates, I don't know, 70 or 90 or something.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:59.72,0:25:03.96,Default,,0,0,0,,So people, you see how popular falsehood is?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:03.96,0:25:10.55,Default,,0,0,0,,People close to half the population still believe that fiction is truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:10.55,0:25:11.29,Default,,0,0,0,,So the Protocol of the Elders of Zion, you know, it's a good thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:11.29,0:25:11.79,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a good thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:11.79,0:25:12.11,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a good thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:12.11,0:25:12.47,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a good thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:12.47,0:25:12.61,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a good thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:12.63,0:25:13.54,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a good thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:13.54,0:25:13.90,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a good thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:13.90,0:25:14.20,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a good thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:14.20,0:25:14.38,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a good thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:14.38,0:25:14.42,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a good thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:14.42,0:25:14.48,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a good thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:14.48,0:25:20.64,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, Henry Ford and a great many people, he printed up copies of it and sent out tens
Dialogue: 0,0:25:20.64,0:25:21.98,Default,,0,0,0,,of thousands.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:21.98,0:25:29.38,Default,,0,0,0,,And anti-Semitism, of course, was part of the fire of the Nazis' hole, the death camps,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:29.38,0:25:30.75,Default,,0,0,0,,et cetera.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:30.75,0:25:32.31,Default,,0,0,0,,So they're not just innocent.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:32.31,0:25:33.63,Default,,0,0,0,,You say, oh, that's just fiction.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:33.63,0:25:35.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:35.18,0:25:36.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Just fiction.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:36.62,0:25:39.96,Default,,0,0,0,,100 million people died in World War II.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:39.96,0:25:42.20,Default,,0,0,0,,100 million people.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:42.20,0:25:44.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Protocol of the Elders of Zion.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:44.04,0:25:51.67,Default,,0,0,0,,It was part of the engine that drove it, hatred, picturing Jews as worms and, you know,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:51.67,0:25:54.33,Default,,0,0,0,,the propaganda films.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:54.33,0:26:01.86,Default,,0,0,0,,So therefore, that which pretends to be truth but is really fiction and fallacy, you can
Dialogue: 0,0:26:01.86,0:26:06.86,Default,,0,0,0,,see, can be quite dangerous to life, quite devastating.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:06.86,0:26:13.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Therefore, to know the truth or the falsehood about a matter is critical, and the one reason
Dialogue: 0,0:26:13.14,0:26:14.46,Default,,0,0,0,,so few people become actually enlightened.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:14.46,0:26:19.96,Default,,0,0,0,,In human life, it's because the way is strewn with falsehood.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:19.96,0:26:28.53,Default,,0,0,0,,You can spend lifetimes going down these byways and following weird cults, et cetera.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:28.53,0:26:33.76,Default,,0,0,0,,So it's important to see what is the impact of falsehood.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:33.76,0:26:34.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Protocol of the Elders of Zion.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:34.76,0:26:40.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure some of these things that are current are having the same negative effect in other
Dialogue: 0,0:26:40.24,0:26:41.98,Default,,0,0,0,,ways.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:41.98,0:26:43.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Aurelians, of course, are based on extraterrestrials.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:43.24,0:26:44.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:44.24,0:26:45.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:45.24,0:26:45.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:45.93,0:26:46.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:46.93,0:26:51.37,Default,,0,0,0,,The idea that reincarnate is a lesser species, I have respect for it because of its ancient
Dialogue: 0,0:26:51.37,0:26:52.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Hindu tradition.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:52.37,0:26:54.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me ask if I have permission.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:54.37,0:27:00.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I have permission to ask about reincarnation as a lesser species.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:00.36,0:27:02.95,Default,,0,0,0,,That is a fact, resist.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:02.95,0:27:04.73,Default,,0,0,0,,It does happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:04.73,0:27:10.43,Default,,0,0,0,,It does not happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:10.43,0:27:17.07,Default,,0,0,0,,It is possible to reincarnate, oh, I see, for humans to reincarnate at a lesser species,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:17.07,0:27:19.10,Default,,0,0,0,,resist.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:19.10,0:27:22.66,Default,,0,0,0,,We've always gotten no on that.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:22.66,0:27:31.97,Default,,0,0,0,,It's possible for a human who has certain karma to reincarnate on this plane as a lesser
Dialogue: 0,0:27:31.97,0:27:32.97,Default,,0,0,0,,animal species.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:32.97,0:27:34.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Resist.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:34.04,0:27:35.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't that funny?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:35.71,0:27:36.71,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:36.71,0:27:37.71,Default,,0,0,0,,You might not be asking it right.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:37.71,0:27:38.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I may not have been asking it the same way.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:38.71,0:27:39.71,Default,,0,0,0,,We've always gotten that it is not so.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:39.71,0:27:49.00,Default,,0,0,0,,However, I have respect for the Hindu, the ancient Hindu knowingness and tradition and
Dialogue: 0,0:27:49.00,0:27:52.00,Default,,0,0,0,,spiritual awareness which says that it does happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:52.00,0:27:53.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, I have no objection to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:53.00,0:27:54.00,Default,,0,0,0,,You know what I'm saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:54.00,0:27:58.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I say we're up to four cats now.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:58.00,0:28:04.18,Default,,0,0,0,,We've only got 60 to go to hit the record, the Johnson record here.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:04.18,0:28:10.44,Default,,0,0,0,,We're learning more and more about multiple cats.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:10.44,0:28:14.46,Default,,0,0,0,,So we'll have to research that further.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:14.46,0:28:20.56,Default,,0,0,0,,So when we get a paradox like that, when we're alone, we will have to retrack why we got
Dialogue: 0,0:28:20.56,0:28:23.56,Default,,0,0,0,,that at that time, why we got this at this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:23.56,0:28:25.56,Default,,0,0,0,,So we will have to research the mystery.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:25.56,0:28:27.13,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:27.13,0:28:28.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Reincarnation.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:28.13,0:28:37.84,Default,,0,0,0,,So is the current reincarnation of the Buddha, Ram, Baha, Dara, Bhajan and that is not so.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:37.84,0:28:41.87,Default,,0,0,0,,The Shroud of Turin we've said before is also fake.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:41.87,0:28:47.16,Default,,0,0,0,,The book The Snake Pit I put in for the same reason as some of these others.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:47.16,0:28:56.16,Default,,0,0,0,,The devastating effect of a book of falsehood like The Snake Pit is the fallout is tremendous.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:56.16,0:29:03.64,Default,,0,0,0,,You create a false picture of reality.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:03.64,0:29:05.64,Default,,0,0,0,,The public buys it.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:05.64,0:29:11.64,Default,,0,0,0,,The political groups then group behind it.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:11.64,0:29:15.64,Default,,0,0,0,,And the next thing you know, you have social destruction right in front of your eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:15.64,0:29:22.98,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, I practiced psychiatry for 50 years in every possible way.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:22.98,0:29:25.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Giant state hospitals, private practice.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:25.98,0:29:27.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I had the largest psychiatric practice.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:27.98,0:29:28.98,Default,,0,0,0,,United States.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:28.98,0:29:36.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I've served as New York State Department of Mental Hygiene, supervising psychiatrists.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:36.20,0:29:39.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I've seen every aspect of psychiatry from left to right.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:39.20,0:29:41.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Private hospital, public hospital.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:41.20,0:29:47.62,Default,,0,0,0,,None of what you see in these horrible things like The Snake Pit occurs.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:47.62,0:29:49.62,Default,,0,0,0,,It's all fallacious.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:49.62,0:29:57.68,Default,,0,0,0,,The recount of an ex-patient from a hospital that comes out paranoid is because they're paranoid.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:57.68,0:29:59.68,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why they were in the pokey.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:59.68,0:30:07.72,Default,,0,0,0,,No, the psychiatrists were not experimenting on them, etc.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:07.72,0:30:08.72,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:08.72,0:30:09.72,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:09.72,0:30:11.72,Default,,0,0,0,,But what is the effect of this kind of thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:11.72,0:30:13.72,Default,,0,0,0,,What the effect of that was?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:13.72,0:30:18.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, it was really the combination of relativism plus things like The Snake Pit.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:18.72,0:30:21.79,Default,,0,0,0,,What happened is that the hospitals emptied out.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:21.79,0:30:22.79,Default,,0,0,0,,See?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:22.79,0:30:28.79,Default,,0,0,0,,And now the mentally ill wander the streets where they get no treatment, no dental care,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:28.79,0:30:29.79,Default,,0,0,0,,no health care.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:29.79,0:30:31.79,Default,,0,0,0,,No nutritionist care.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:31.79,0:30:32.79,Default,,0,0,0,,No counseling.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:32.79,0:30:34.79,Default,,0,0,0,,No psychiatric meds.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:34.79,0:30:35.79,Default,,0,0,0,,No doctor.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:35.79,0:30:40.82,Default,,0,0,0,,No protection from being savaged by the lower elements.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:40.82,0:30:50.46,Default,,0,0,0,,And the old-fashioned state hospital, which I knew extremely well, was a home and a source of protection.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:50.46,0:30:53.46,Default,,0,0,0,,And it was its own community where everybody understood each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:53.46,0:30:56.59,Default,,0,0,0,,And they just accepted you for who you were.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:56.59,0:30:59.59,Default,,0,0,0,,And if you got well enough to get out, the hospital was glad to get rid of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:59.59,0:31:02.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, the hospital didn't make money on patients.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:02.59,0:31:03.59,Default,,0,0,0,,We were a state hospital.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:03.59,0:31:04.59,Default,,0,0,0,,We got paid by the bed.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:04.59,0:31:07.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Whether the bed was full or not, we didn't care.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:07.72,0:31:10.72,Default,,0,0,0,,So, there was no reason, etc.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:10.72,0:31:13.00,Default,,0,0,0,,So, a great tragedy came out of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:13.00,0:31:17.00,Default,,0,0,0,,And now you see how the mentally ill are in everyday's paper.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:17.00,0:31:24.00,Default,,0,0,0,,They're involved in burglary and drugs and rape and starve to death on the streets and
Dialogue: 0,0:31:24.00,0:31:29.00,Default,,0,0,0,,become savaged and, of course, are addicted to drugs and alcohol.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:29.00,0:31:37.74,Default,,0,0,0,,So, what was a nurturing environment, the old state hospital, I calibrated it at, what, 350 or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:37.74,0:31:38.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:38.74,0:31:40.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Positive, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:40.80,0:31:45.80,Default,,0,0,0,,And now the street culture calibrates, you know, about 110 or something like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:45.80,0:31:46.80,Default,,0,0,0,,About 110.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:46.80,0:31:52.80,Default,,0,0,0,,So, what they did is take them out of a safe, protective environment that had hope for the future
Dialogue: 0,0:31:52.80,0:31:56.80,Default,,0,0,0,,and threw them on the street where they have no hope for the future.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:56.80,0:31:58.80,Default,,0,0,0,,And that was primarily the result of falsehood.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:58.80,0:32:03.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Snake Fit, there was another movie like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:03.80,0:32:14.12,Default,,0,0,0,,And Scientology picked up on that anti-establishment, psychiatrist, wicked, same trick, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:14.12,0:32:18.12,Default,,0,0,0,,And, of course, all of that was also fueled by relativism.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:18.12,0:32:27.34,Default,,0,0,0,,And relativism, some of the best philosophers behind relativism, I'm ashamed to say, were psychiatrists.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:27.34,0:32:29.37,Default,,0,0,0,,And so, that kind of thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:29.37,0:32:34.37,Default,,0,0,0,,So, that kind of thinking, that kind of thinking then, putting the blame on somebody, et cetera.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:34.37,0:32:39.37,Default,,0,0,0,,So, relativism, I don't want to get off on because that's a whole lecture in itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:39.37,0:32:43.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Reincarnation of the Buddha, that's not the Buddha reincarnated there, despite the papers.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:43.76,0:32:47.76,Default,,0,0,0,,The Shroud of Turin, as we said, this book had a very injurious.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:47.76,0:32:54.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Solar Temple is, I forget the name of that guy, he's esoteric.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:54.76,0:32:57.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Starseed Children, Transmedium Chip.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:57.95,0:32:58.95,Default,,0,0,0,,We said UFO.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:58.95,0:33:01.95,Default,,0,0,0,,We said UFOs, UFO religions.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:01.95,0:33:03.95,Default,,0,0,0,,And everybody asked me about the Urantia book.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:03.95,0:33:07.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I hate to tell them that it's only 150, but that's a fact.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:07.95,0:33:09.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I've rechecked it over and over again.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:09.95,0:33:11.95,Default,,0,0,0,,And I know lots of people like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:11.95,0:33:12.95,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a very thick book.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:12.95,0:33:16.95,Default,,0,0,0,,It'll keep you entertained for a few years.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:16.95,0:33:20.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Another Dimension, in which they claim Christ is part of the other dimension.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:20.95,0:33:24.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought, that's interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:24.13,0:33:27.23,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, it's just good to know about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:27.23,0:33:29.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Because the pitfalls along the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:30.23,0:33:34.23,Default,,0,0,0,,The attraction of these things appeals to the curious child in us.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:34.23,0:33:37.23,Default,,0,0,0,,The child in us is innocent.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:37.23,0:33:43.23,Default,,0,0,0,,So the child in us is both our salvation and our downfall.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:43.23,0:33:44.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:44.93,0:33:49.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Because spiritual progress is only made by faith.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:49.25,0:33:52.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Made by faith and trust.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:52.70,0:33:55.70,Default,,0,0,0,,In fact, we don't know anything except by faith and trust.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:55.70,0:34:00.70,Default,,0,0,0,,So faith and trust is intrinsic to the human mentality.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:00.70,0:34:02.70,Default,,0,0,0,,It arises in children.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:02.70,0:34:10.97,Default,,0,0,0,,The human mind, because it can't tell essence from perception,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:10.97,0:34:18.45,Default,,0,0,0,,is extremely naive and innocent and vulnerable, therefore, to falsehood and to error.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:18.45,0:34:25.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Faith and trust are the basics by which all spiritual progress is made.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:25.06,0:34:27.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, that's the problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:27.06,0:34:30.06,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the wonderful thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:30.06,0:34:32.06,Default,,0,0,0,,That's also the downside.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:32.06,0:34:38.06,Default,,0,0,0,,The downside why nobody gets enlightened is because it is innocent and naive.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:38.06,0:34:40.06,Default,,0,0,0,,It can't tell truth from falsehood.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:40.06,0:34:45.25,Default,,0,0,0,,And it buys falsehood because of its basic innocence.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:45.25,0:34:52.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Without that basic capacity for trust and faith, spiritual progress is not possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:52.25,0:34:55.25,Default,,0,0,0,,So, first of all, it's a requirement.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:55.25,0:35:02.38,Default,,0,0,0,,On the other hand, it has faith and trust in illusion with the same tenacity it does in truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:02.38,0:35:07.41,Default,,0,0,0,,So the mind, unaided, is unable to discern truth from falsehood.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:07.41,0:35:09.41,Default,,0,0,0,,The human mind, unaided.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:09.41,0:35:13.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Anybody doubt that?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:13.43,0:35:14.43,Default,,0,0,0,,The Buddha's not here today.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:14.43,0:35:16.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:16.43,0:35:27.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Therefore, all the great teachers have said there's only one human error and that is ignorance.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:27.06,0:35:30.09,Default,,0,0,0,,The ignorance, unfortunately, is inborn.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:30.09,0:35:33.09,Default,,0,0,0,,It's intrinsic to the human condition.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:33.09,0:35:38.16,Default,,0,0,0,,So we're here, you know, to transcend what is an intrinsic,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:38.16,0:35:44.19,Default,,0,0,0,,on the one hand, defect, and on the other hand, it's the road to enlightenment.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:44.19,0:35:51.20,Default,,0,0,0,,There are 10,000 ways to God, as I said, and we've covered quite a few of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:51.20,0:35:55.20,Default,,0,0,0,,For any of them to work, you have to have faith and confidence and trust.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:55.20,0:36:00.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Faith, confidence, and trust in today's world has been ravaged, ravaged.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:00.20,0:36:07.20,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a wonder to me that anybody is still capable of faith and trust,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:07.20,0:36:09.20,Default,,0,0,0,,seeing as...
Dialogue: 0,0:36:10.20,0:36:14.20,Default,,0,0,0,,the fallacy that goes on in the media,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:14.20,0:36:18.20,Default,,0,0,0,,just, you know, ordinary media, just the ordinary media.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:18.20,0:36:21.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's see.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:21.20,0:36:25.20,Default,,0,0,0,,The newspaper I have in mind, I can calibrate the editorial pages.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:25.20,0:36:28.97,Default,,0,0,0,,It's over 190, 195.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:28.97,0:36:32.97,Default,,0,0,0,,New York Times editorial page is currently calibrated 190.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:32.97,0:36:35.97,Default,,0,0,0,,So, as much as truth starts at 200,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:35.97,0:36:40.23,Default,,0,0,0,,what hope is there for mankind? I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:41.23,0:36:44.23,Default,,0,0,0,,What hope is there for mankind?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:44.23,0:36:48.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Surrounded by fallacy, the human mind, unaided,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:48.23,0:36:52.09,Default,,0,0,0,,is unable to discern truth from falsehood.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:52.09,0:36:58.34,Default,,0,0,0,,And then, of course, within that is the innocence of the child
Dialogue: 0,0:36:58.34,0:37:04.53,Default,,0,0,0,,that has a provisional faith and trust in everything as it crosses their vision.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:04.53,0:37:06.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Faith and trust.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:06.82,0:37:10.82,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the faith and trust that grows out of the child's dependence on the parent.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:10.82,0:37:12.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Therefore, it is contextualized,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:12.82,0:37:16.85,Default,,0,0,0,,contextualized as necessary for survival.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:16.85,0:37:19.20,Default,,0,0,0,,You have to have faith and trust.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:19.20,0:37:24.20,Default,,0,0,0,,So, you see the tremendous importance of being able to discern truth from falsehood.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:24.20,0:37:30.43,Default,,0,0,0,,So, the gift I was given, unasked, was suddenly out of nothing seeing it.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:30.43,0:37:33.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Suddenly out of nothing seeing, for the first time,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:33.49,0:37:37.49,Default,,0,0,0,,the discernment of truth to falsehood in all of human history.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:37.49,0:37:40.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow. What a responsibility.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:40.65,0:37:41.65,Default,,0,0,0,,You know what I'm saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:41.65,0:37:42.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Gee whiz.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:43.65,0:37:47.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I can see what's going to happen to the rest of my life
Dialogue: 0,0:37:47.45,0:37:49.45,Default,,0,0,0,,because you can't exactly just ignore that.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:49.45,0:37:56.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Dedicated to demonstrating it, calibrating it, explaining it, documenting it,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:56.84,0:38:01.00,Default,,0,0,0,,and then doing it thousands of times,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:01.00,0:38:05.00,Default,,0,0,0,,and then sharing it with everyone for the long-term benefit.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:05.00,0:38:10.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you wish you had a list like this for your stocks, stock market, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:15.22,0:38:21.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you wish you knew the winners and the losers, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:21.02,0:38:29.34,Default,,0,0,0,,So, the value then of knowing truth from falsehood is that it saves many lifetimes.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:29.34,0:38:33.34,Default,,0,0,0,,The likelihood of becoming enlightened in today's world,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:33.34,0:38:39.34,Default,,0,0,0,,as we have said before, by today's world I mean the information that we share here,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:39.34,0:38:45.34,Default,,0,0,0,,is 1,000 times greater than before this information was available.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:45.34,0:38:49.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Chances of becoming enlightened are 1,000 times greater
Dialogue: 0,0:38:49.34,0:38:54.50,Default,,0,0,0,,because you now have a pathway that's been searched like,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:54.50,0:38:56.50,Default,,0,0,0,,you know, we've looked at this pathway we searched like,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:56.50,0:38:58.50,Default,,0,0,0,,and we've verified it.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:58.50,0:39:02.50,Default,,0,0,0,,We've already made the trip ahead of time that it's a safe pathway
Dialogue: 0,0:39:02.50,0:39:04.50,Default,,0,0,0,,and that it takes you to truth
Dialogue: 0,0:39:04.50,0:39:07.50,Default,,0,0,0,,and that you can verify your trip all along the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:07.50,0:39:13.49,Default,,0,0,0,,So, the value of consciousness research is for the first time it gave us a compass
Dialogue: 0,0:39:13.49,0:39:16.49,Default,,0,0,0,,and the mankind before was like a sailor with a boat
Dialogue: 0,0:39:16.49,0:39:18.56,Default,,0,0,0,,without a compass.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:18.56,0:39:21.56,Default,,0,0,0,,And hopefully this was the right direction
Dialogue: 0,0:39:21.56,0:39:23.56,Default,,0,0,0,,and hopefully that was the right direction,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:23.56,0:39:26.56,Default,,0,0,0,,but the number of ships at the bottom of the sea,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:26.56,0:39:28.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I remember a program on the Great Lakes,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:28.56,0:39:30.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I can hardly believe it,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:30.56,0:39:33.56,Default,,0,0,0,,there are 6,000 ships at the bottom of the Great Lakes alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:33.56,0:39:35.56,Default,,0,0,0,,6,000, just the Great Lakes.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:35.56,0:39:38.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Imagine what it must be in the oceans.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:38.56,0:39:41.56,Default,,0,0,0,,All from not having a compass, not knowing which way you're going
Dialogue: 0,0:39:41.56,0:39:45.56,Default,,0,0,0,,and not being able to control your own destiny, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:45.56,0:39:48.56,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't control your own destiny, but you can certainly set up likelihoods.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:48.56,0:39:50.81,Default,,0,0,0,,So, by devotion to truth,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:50.81,0:39:52.81,Default,,0,0,0,,and that's the reason for the title,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:52.81,0:39:54.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Devotional Non-duality.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:54.81,0:39:56.81,Default,,0,0,0,,By devotion to truth,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:56.81,0:39:58.81,Default,,0,0,0,,you bring to yourself,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:58.81,0:40:01.81,Default,,0,0,0,,you now bring to yourself information
Dialogue: 0,0:40:01.81,0:40:05.81,Default,,0,0,0,,and the capacity to understand things that did not exist before.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:05.81,0:40:09.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Because intention is very powerful.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:09.20,0:40:11.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Your intention to become enlightened,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:11.20,0:40:13.20,Default,,0,0,0,,your intention to know the truth,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:13.20,0:40:15.20,Default,,0,0,0,,to transcend negativity, etc.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:15.20,0:40:20.20,Default,,0,0,0,,That intention alone already begins to change the effects.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:20.20,0:40:23.20,Default,,0,0,0,,And we know that's been supported by advanced theoretical physics,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:23.20,0:40:27.32,Default,,0,0,0,,the Heisenberg Principle.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:27.32,0:40:29.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Other things that we've said here that are outrageous,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:29.32,0:40:32.32,Default,,0,0,0,,and some things I haven't even said them because they are too outrageous.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:36.85,0:40:39.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I wait till there's some corroboration out there and then I say it.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:39.85,0:40:42.85,Default,,0,0,0,,But I did say, you know, one of the books or lectures somewhere,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:42.85,0:40:46.85,Default,,0,0,0,,that even time and position in space
Dialogue: 0,0:40:46.85,0:40:48.85,Default,,0,0,0,,are projections.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:48.85,0:40:51.85,Default,,0,0,0,,They have no independent existence.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:51.85,0:40:54.85,Default,,0,0,0,,There isn't such a thing as time in reality.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:54.85,0:40:58.88,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a projection that we put onto a sequence.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:58.88,0:41:00.88,Default,,0,0,0,,We see sequence, therefore we call it time,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:00.88,0:41:02.88,Default,,0,0,0,,and see it as sequential.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:02.88,0:41:05.88,Default,,0,0,0,,So, the latest thing that I read recently
Dialogue: 0,0:41:05.88,0:41:08.88,Default,,0,0,0,,in the advanced theoretical physics
Dialogue: 0,0:41:08.88,0:41:10.92,Default,,0,0,0,,is by...
Dialogue: 0,0:41:10.92,0:41:12.92,Default,,0,0,0,,is by...
Dialogue: 0,0:41:12.92,0:41:15.56,Default,,0,0,0,,is by...
Dialogue: 0,0:41:15.56,0:41:18.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know who it's by.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:18.68,0:41:22.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway, it'll come to me who it's by.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:22.44,0:41:25.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway, it'll come to me who it's by.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:25.44,0:41:28.44,Default,,0,0,0,,And it jumps that advanced theoretical physics is now...
Dialogue: 0,0:41:28.44,0:41:31.44,Default,,0,0,0,,And it jumps that advanced theoretical physics is now...
Dialogue: 0,0:41:31.44,0:41:33.51,Default,,0,0,0,,It'll come to me the name.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:33.51,0:41:36.51,Default,,0,0,0,,It comes to the conclusion that time,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:36.51,0:41:39.51,Default,,0,0,0,,in fact, any periods of time, etc.,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:39.51,0:41:42.51,Default,,0,0,0,,are all projections from consciousness,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:42.51,0:41:45.51,Default,,0,0,0,,which is what we've said all along.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:45.51,0:41:48.51,Default,,0,0,0,,That time and sequence and all those are all projections
Dialogue: 0,0:41:48.51,0:41:50.51,Default,,0,0,0,,within reality.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:50.51,0:41:53.51,Default,,0,0,0,,All things are emerging.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:53.51,0:41:55.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Because what you're seeing
Dialogue: 0,0:41:55.51,0:41:58.51,Default,,0,0,0,,is potentiality becoming actuality
Dialogue: 0,0:41:58.51,0:42:02.67,Default,,0,0,0,,when it's energized by intention,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:02.67,0:42:05.34,Default,,0,0,0,,especially by intention.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:05.34,0:42:07.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Potentiality becomes actuality
Dialogue: 0,0:42:07.34,0:42:10.34,Default,,0,0,0,,and, therefore, becomes experiential.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:10.34,0:42:13.60,Default,,0,0,0,,The potential, therefore, for enlightenment
Dialogue: 0,0:42:13.60,0:42:15.60,Default,,0,0,0,,resides within everyone here.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:15.60,0:42:17.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's check to make sure there's no...
Dialogue: 0,0:42:17.66,0:42:18.66,Default,,0,0,0,,You know what's here.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:18.66,0:42:21.88,Default,,0,0,0,,You know what's here.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:21.88,0:42:25.29,Default,,0,0,0,,It's 100% for this audience.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:25.29,0:42:27.64,Default,,0,0,0,,That means you.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:27.64,0:42:28.64,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:28.64,0:42:31.28,Default,,0,0,0,,For some reason, this group selected,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:31.28,0:42:34.51,Default,,0,0,0,,self-selected, have come together
Dialogue: 0,0:42:34.51,0:42:36.51,Default,,0,0,0,,because they have sensed,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:36.51,0:42:39.51,Default,,0,0,0,,probably by karmic something or other,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:39.51,0:42:42.18,Default,,0,0,0,,that...
Dialogue: 0,0:42:42.18,0:42:44.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know. I can't remember the name of that.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:44.18,0:42:45.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:45.47,0:42:47.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Peter Lind. L-Y-N-D.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:47.47,0:42:48.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Peter.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:48.72,0:42:50.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Quantum mechanics study.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:50.72,0:42:51.72,Default,,0,0,0,,So, Peter Lind.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:51.72,0:42:52.72,Default,,0,0,0,,He's on the e-mail...
Dialogue: 0,0:42:52.72,0:42:53.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Internet thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:53.72,0:42:56.72,Default,,0,0,0,,The W-W-W machine thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:56.72,0:42:57.72,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a...
Dialogue: 0,0:42:57.72,0:42:59.49,Default,,0,0,0,,You put...
Dialogue: 0,0:42:59.49,0:43:00.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Lynch, Peter.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:00.49,0:43:01.49,Default,,0,0,0,,No, what is his name?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:01.49,0:43:02.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:02.49,0:43:04.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway, you put it in there.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:04.04,0:43:05.04,Default,,0,0,0,,And then you get...
Dialogue: 0,0:43:05.04,0:43:07.04,Default,,0,0,0,,You get the whole printout.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:07.04,0:43:08.04,Default,,0,0,0,,It's very interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:08.04,0:43:10.23,Default,,0,0,0,,L-Y-N-D. Peter.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:10.23,0:43:14.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Quantum mechanics confirms
Dialogue: 0,0:43:14.36,0:43:16.71,Default,,0,0,0,,our own consciousness studies.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:16.71,0:43:19.71,Default,,0,0,0,,That time itself is a projection.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:19.71,0:43:23.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Consequently, as you see from this morning,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:23.06,0:43:25.12,Default,,0,0,0,,this slide,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:25.12,0:43:28.12,Default,,0,0,0,,all things about the future
Dialogue: 0,0:43:28.12,0:43:30.99,Default,,0,0,0,,make your arm go weak.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:30.99,0:43:32.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Man, we just got confirmation of that
Dialogue: 0,0:43:32.99,0:43:34.99,Default,,0,0,0,,from quantum mechanics.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:34.99,0:43:36.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Didn't we?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:36.08,0:43:37.08,Default,,0,0,0,,We just got...
Dialogue: 0,0:43:37.08,0:43:40.72,Default,,0,0,0,,If there is no such reality
Dialogue: 0,0:43:40.72,0:43:43.01,Default,,0,0,0,,as time,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:43.01,0:43:46.01,Default,,0,0,0,,then how can we predict what's in the future
Dialogue: 0,0:43:46.01,0:43:49.01,Default,,0,0,0,,as much as time doesn't exist
Dialogue: 0,0:43:49.01,0:43:50.01,Default,,0,0,0,,as a reality?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:50.01,0:43:51.01,Default,,0,0,0,,You understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:51.01,0:43:52.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Therefore,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:52.01,0:43:54.01,Default,,0,0,0,,all projections about the future are fantasy.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:54.01,0:43:56.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Our fantasies.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:56.11,0:43:57.11,Default,,0,0,0,,But we said that
Dialogue: 0,0:43:57.11,0:43:59.91,Default,,0,0,0,,critical scientific statement
Dialogue: 0,0:43:59.91,0:44:01.91,Default,,0,0,0,,here a long time ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:01.91,0:44:03.91,Default,,0,0,0,,That the universe that you see
Dialogue: 0,0:44:03.91,0:44:04.91,Default,,0,0,0,,is a projection.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:04.91,0:44:05.91,Default,,0,0,0,,It's evolutionary.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:05.91,0:44:07.91,Default,,0,0,0,,And there's no way of saying
Dialogue: 0,0:44:07.91,0:44:09.91,Default,,0,0,0,,anything about the future.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:09.91,0:44:11.91,Default,,0,0,0,,There's probabilities within
Dialogue: 0,0:44:11.91,0:44:13.91,Default,,0,0,0,,the three-dimensional
Dialogue: 0,0:44:13.91,0:44:15.91,Default,,0,0,0,,linear domain probabilities.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:15.91,0:44:16.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, there is.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:16.91,0:44:18.91,Default,,0,0,0,,But it's not causal.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:18.91,0:44:22.06,Default,,0,0,0,,It's each thing being
Dialogue: 0,0:44:22.06,0:44:24.06,Default,,0,0,0,,the fullest of what it can be
Dialogue: 0,0:44:24.06,0:44:25.06,Default,,0,0,0,,in the future.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:25.06,0:44:27.06,Default,,0,0,0,,The fullest of what it can be
Dialogue: 0,0:44:27.06,0:44:29.32,Default,,0,0,0,,when local conditions are appropriate.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:29.32,0:44:30.32,Default,,0,0,0,,So if there's no time,
Dialogue: 0,0:44:30.32,0:44:32.32,Default,,0,0,0,,then neither are there intervals.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:32.32,0:44:35.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Neither is there any such thing as now.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:35.32,0:44:38.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Neither is there any such thing as then.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:38.32,0:44:40.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Or the future or the past.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:40.32,0:44:41.32,Default,,0,0,0,,These are all
Dialogue: 0,0:44:41.32,0:44:43.32,Default,,0,0,0,,which way you're running the film.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:43.32,0:44:44.32,Default,,0,0,0,,You can run it backwards
Dialogue: 0,0:44:44.32,0:44:46.32,Default,,0,0,0,,and you can run it forwards.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:46.32,0:44:48.32,Default,,0,0,0,,But that's just a readout.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:48.32,0:44:49.32,Default,,0,0,0,,And no such thing exists
Dialogue: 0,0:44:49.32,0:44:51.32,Default,,0,0,0,,in reality with a capital R.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:51.32,0:44:53.32,Default,,0,0,0,,In reality with a capital R.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:53.32,0:44:55.54,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no past, present, and future.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:55.54,0:44:56.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:56.54,0:44:58.54,Default,,0,0,0,,And there is no such thing as time.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:58.54,0:45:01.02,Default,,0,0,0,,So, um,
Dialogue: 0,0:45:01.02,0:45:03.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought I'll send Peter,
Dialogue: 0,0:45:03.34,0:45:04.34,Default,,0,0,0,,what is his name again?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:04.34,0:45:05.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Lynn?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:05.34,0:45:06.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:08.88,0:45:09.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know how to do an email.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:09.88,0:45:10.88,Default,,0,0,0,,So I tell the girl,
Dialogue: 0,0:45:10.88,0:45:11.88,Default,,0,0,0,,send him an email and say
Dialogue: 0,0:45:11.88,0:45:12.88,Default,,0,0,0,,we think it's great
Dialogue: 0,0:45:12.88,0:45:13.88,Default,,0,0,0,,and we have certain corroboration
Dialogue: 0,0:45:13.88,0:45:14.88,Default,,0,0,0,,if you'd like to know.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:14.88,0:45:17.00,Default,,0,0,0,,We've never been agreeing with him
Dialogue: 0,0:45:17.00,0:45:18.00,Default,,0,0,0,,all along from the viewpoint
Dialogue: 0,0:45:18.00,0:45:19.00,Default,,0,0,0,,of consciousness.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:19.00,0:45:21.00,Default,,0,0,0,,So this is the first time that,
Dialogue: 0,0:45:21.00,0:45:23.00,Default,,0,0,0,,other than the Heisenberg principle,
Dialogue: 0,0:45:23.00,0:45:26.00,Default,,0,0,0,,that advanced theoretical physics,
Dialogue: 0,0:45:26.00,0:45:27.00,Default,,0,0,0,,quantum mechanics, etc.,
Dialogue: 0,0:45:27.00,0:45:29.00,Default,,0,0,0,,is being looked at strictly
Dialogue: 0,0:45:29.00,0:45:31.00,Default,,0,0,0,,from the viewpoint of consciousness.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:31.00,0:45:33.00,Default,,0,0,0,,From the viewpoint of consciousness,
Dialogue: 0,0:45:33.00,0:45:35.00,Default,,0,0,0,,no such thing is possible
Dialogue: 0,0:45:35.00,0:45:38.00,Default,,0,0,0,,as time and therefore interval.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:38.00,0:45:40.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't that interesting?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:40.00,0:45:42.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:42.06,0:45:43.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I know on your way home
Dialogue: 0,0:45:43.06,0:45:45.06,Default,,0,0,0,,you'll be happy without it.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:47.86,0:45:48.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Doc made my day.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:48.86,0:45:49.86,Default,,0,0,0,,You know what he said?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:53.92,0:45:55.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I just think it's interesting
Dialogue: 0,0:45:55.08,0:45:56.08,Default,,0,0,0,,when we get corroboration
Dialogue: 0,0:45:56.08,0:45:57.08,Default,,0,0,0,,from other fields.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:57.08,0:45:58.08,Default,,0,0,0,,So the closest thing
Dialogue: 0,0:45:58.08,0:45:59.08,Default,,0,0,0,,within the linear domain,
Dialogue: 0,0:45:59.08,0:46:00.08,Default,,0,0,0,,scientific domain,
Dialogue: 0,0:46:00.08,0:46:01.08,Default,,0,0,0,,and what we talk about
Dialogue: 0,0:46:01.08,0:46:02.08,Default,,0,0,0,,is actually quantum mechanics
Dialogue: 0,0:46:02.08,0:46:03.08,Default,,0,0,0,,and advanced theoretical physics
Dialogue: 0,0:46:03.08,0:46:04.08,Default,,0,0,0,,is pretty well correlated.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:04.08,0:46:05.08,Default,,0,0,0,,We're pretty well correlated.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:05.08,0:46:06.08,Default,,0,0,0,,And this sort of puts in
Dialogue: 0,0:46:06.08,0:46:07.08,Default,,0,0,0,,the last missing link.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:07.08,0:46:08.08,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:08.08,0:46:09.08,Default,,0,0,0,,So I want to go back
Dialogue: 0,0:46:09.08,0:46:10.08,Default,,0,0,0,,to the slides.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:10.08,0:46:11.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Is there any question
Dialogue: 0,0:46:11.08,0:46:12.08,Default,,0,0,0,,about what we've spoken
Dialogue: 0,0:46:12.08,0:46:13.08,Default,,0,0,0,,about this morning?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:13.08,0:46:14.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Anybody have doubts?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:14.18,0:46:15.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it okay with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:15.18,0:46:16.18,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:16.18,0:46:17.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Somebody wrote
Dialogue: 0,0:46:17.18,0:46:18.18,Default,,0,0,0,,the repeater question to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:18.18,0:46:19.18,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:19.18,0:46:20.18,Default,,0,0,0,,.
