Dialogue: 0,0:47:07.72,0:47:08.72,Default,,0,0,0,,.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:08.72,0:47:09.72,Default,,0,0,0,,.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:09.72,0:47:10.72,Default,,0,0,0,,.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:10.72,0:47:11.72,Default,,0,0,0,,.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:11.72,0:47:16.37,Default,,0,0,0,,.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:16.37,0:47:17.37,Default,,0,0,0,,.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:17.37,0:47:25.62,Default,,0,0,0,,a compulsive worrywart. She just never surrendered and did the course. So the Course in Miracles
Dialogue: 0,0:47:25.62,0:47:29.62,Default,,0,0,0,,itself is unique. You know, you could do a lot of research on it and discover a lot of
Dialogue: 0,0:47:29.62,0:47:35.28,Default,,0,0,0,,things about it. All I'm interested in is that it's practical and that it works. It's
Dialogue: 0,0:47:35.28,0:47:39.74,Default,,0,0,0,,practical and it works. And of course, a lot of people do it along with other things. You
Dialogue: 0,0:47:39.74,0:47:44.46,Default,,0,0,0,,know, you do this, that, and you also do the Course in Miracles. And many people, of course,
Dialogue: 0,0:47:44.46,0:47:50.24,Default,,0,0,0,,have recovered from many illnesses. In the clinic back east, you know, we had the second
Dialogue: 0,0:47:50.24,0:47:56.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Attitudinal Healing Center in the United States. The first was in Tiburon. And we had the second
Dialogue: 0,0:47:56.55,0:48:01.75,Default,,0,0,0,,in the United States. And we saw, you know, miraculous recoveries from all kinds of things.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:02.49,0:48:08.47,Default,,0,0,0,,All kinds of things. All kinds of non-recoverable illnesses. If you do the Course in Miracles,
Dialogue: 0,0:48:08.67,0:48:12.17,Default,,0,0,0,,you won't care whether you're, if you've done it, if you've really done the Course in Miracles,
Dialogue: 0,0:48:12.87,0:48:14.63,Default,,0,0,0,,whether you recover physically or
Dialogue: 0,0:48:14.63,0:48:21.83,Default,,0,0,0,,not is irrelevant. In the beginning, you're trying to control it. You know, you've got
Dialogue: 0,0:48:21.83,0:48:25.45,Default,,0,0,0,,karmic consequences all over the place, and you're going to try and control it. Yeah,
Dialogue: 0,0:48:25.49,0:48:31.41,Default,,0,0,0,,right. So if you do the Course in Miracles, you surrender at such a depth that whether
Dialogue: 0,0:48:31.41,0:48:37.19,Default,,0,0,0,,this illness disappears or not is, you know, academic. It's nice if it does. I can leave
Dialogue: 0,0:48:37.19,0:48:41.83,Default,,0,0,0,,the crutches home. And if you don't, I'll keep the crutches, you know. So when you've
Dialogue: 0,0:48:41.83,0:48:45.25,Default,,0,0,0,,really done the Course in Miracles, you've completely surrendered to the Course in Miracles.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:45.25,0:48:50.77,Default,,0,0,0,,You've surrendered it to God and to God's will. And you see it differently, that it's
Dialogue: 0,0:48:50.77,0:48:57.83,Default,,0,0,0,,the fulfillment of some potential that is of great benefit. So therefore, to really
Dialogue: 0,0:48:57.83,0:49:03.93,Default,,0,0,0,,do the Course in order to recover, that's what attracts a lot of people beginning. In
Dialogue: 0,0:49:03.93,0:49:08.95,Default,,0,0,0,,order to recover, they've heard that you can recover from anything with the Course in Miracles,
Dialogue: 0,0:49:09.09,0:49:13.89,Default,,0,0,0,,and I've seen people recover from just about everything. That's a fact. On the other hand,
Dialogue: 0,0:49:13.89,0:49:15.45,Default,,0,0,0,,they also forget karmic prevention.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:15.47,0:49:19.19,Default,,0,0,0,,They don't have the propensities that you may or may not recover doing the Course in
Dialogue: 0,0:49:19.19,0:49:24.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Miracles. However, you've certainly gained a lot of spiritual merit. And I don't suppose
Dialogue: 0,0:49:24.07,0:49:30.35,Default,,0,0,0,,God will be angry that you did the Course in Miracles. That you've applied Christian
Dialogue: 0,0:49:30.35,0:49:36.38,Default,,0,0,0,,principles at a very deep level. It has an effect on other people. The fact that you're
Dialogue: 0,0:49:36.38,0:49:41.80,Default,,0,0,0,,doing the Course has a positive benefit on other people. So the other reason you can
Dialogue: 0,0:49:41.80,0:49:44.80,Default,,0,0,0,,do it is not only just for yourself, but for the good of mankind.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:45.66,0:49:48.68,Default,,0,0,0,,All of us contribute to the advance of human consciousness.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:49.66,0:49:51.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, we keep track on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:52.32,0:49:53.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's track.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:54.24,0:49:57.01,Default,,0,0,0,,The consciousness level of mankind,
Dialogue: 0,0:49:57.27,0:49:58.87,Default,,0,0,0,,we have permission to do it right now,
Dialogue: 0,0:49:59.59,0:50:04.74,Default,,0,0,0,,is over 205, 206, 207.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:05.67,0:50:07.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Went from 207 down to 206.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:07.79,0:50:09.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Went down one point in the last year or two.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:10.55,0:50:15.87,Default,,0,0,0,,In America, it's over 425, 426, 427.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:15.87,0:50:17.65,Default,,0,0,0,,America is staying at 425.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:18.01,0:50:19.35,Default,,0,0,0,,The world went down one point.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:21.66,0:50:21.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Whatever.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:27.89,0:50:29.37,Default,,0,0,0,,424, 425.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:31.36,0:50:32.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Another million die.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:32.38,0:50:33.50,Default,,0,0,0,,One point, millions die.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:33.58,0:50:33.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, well.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:37.86,0:50:38.34,Default,,0,0,0,,It was?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:39.14,0:50:39.74,Default,,0,0,0,,America?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:41.50,0:50:43.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't remember all those.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:43.24,0:50:44.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Didn't we get 426?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:44.88,0:50:45.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:46.44,0:50:48.14,Default,,0,0,0,,And then we did Singapore.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:48.48,0:50:49.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, let's do Singapore again.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:50.53,0:50:54.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Singapore is over 430.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:54.61,0:50:54.97,Default,,0,0,0,,430.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:55.05,0:50:55.49,Default,,0,0,0,,435.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:57.01,0:50:57.41,Default,,0,0,0,,434.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:58.23,0:50:58.71,Default,,0,0,0,,435.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:58.97,0:51:01.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Singapore is 434, and America is 426.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:03.04,0:51:03.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, dear.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:03.94,0:51:04.60,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not right.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:05.76,0:51:08.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Why can't the Singaporean foreigners be ahead of us?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:09.52,0:51:11.59,Default,,0,0,0,,What in the world are they doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:11.69,0:51:12.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's find out.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:14.80,0:51:17.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, if you throw trash on the street,
Dialogue: 0,0:51:17.50,0:51:18.98,Default,,0,0,0,,you get a $50 fine instantly.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:20.32,0:51:23.10,Default,,0,0,0,,No smoking gum, no chewing gum on the sidewalk.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:23.10,0:51:27.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, sounds repressive, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:29.98,0:51:33.89,Default,,0,0,0,,To a libertarian, sounds repressive.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:34.76,0:51:37.08,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't even throw your trash on the street?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:37.42,0:51:38.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Good God.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:38.22,0:51:38.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Where's freedom?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:43.70,0:51:47.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Now freedom of speech has been spread to freedom of action.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:47.82,0:51:49.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Action is symbolic speech.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:51.42,0:51:54.96,Default,,0,0,0,,So, am I right that freedom of speech is to throw trash on the sidewalk?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:56.54,0:51:59.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, that's why they're at four, whatever they are.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:00.20,0:52:01.24,Default,,0,0,0,,We're at four or something.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:02.06,0:52:02.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:02.38,0:52:03.74,Default,,0,0,0,,So, it demonstrates.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:03.74,0:52:05.38,Default,,0,0,0,,It demonstrates things we've written about.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:06.08,0:52:08.38,Default,,0,0,0,,The advantage of an oligarchy, you know,
Dialogue: 0,0:52:08.46,0:52:10.38,Default,,0,0,0,,because Singapore is an oligarchy.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:11.61,0:52:16.25,Default,,0,0,0,,And mankind really existed because of the tribal chiefs, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:16.39,0:52:18.57,Default,,0,0,0,,It was the elders of the tribe.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:19.19,0:52:21.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Most tribes survived because they listened to the elders,
Dialogue: 0,0:52:21.93,0:52:22.71,Default,,0,0,0,,revered the elders.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:23.49,0:52:27.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Many ancient cultures survived because they listened to the elders.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:28.07,0:52:30.97,Default,,0,0,0,,And an oligarchy is one in which a council of the elders
Dialogue: 0,0:52:30.97,0:52:32.77,Default,,0,0,0,,dominates the...
Dialogue: 0,0:52:33.99,0:52:34.99,Default,,0,0,0,,the government.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:35.23,0:52:37.59,Default,,0,0,0,,We have a democracy which calibrates less.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:38.93,0:52:42.13,Default,,0,0,0,,And, of course, as Socrates says, the downside of a democracy
Dialogue: 0,0:52:43.24,0:52:47.62,Default,,0,0,0,,is that 50% of the people in America who calibrate below 200
Dialogue: 0,0:52:47.62,0:52:49.82,Default,,0,0,0,,have an equal vote to the 200 above, you see.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:51.77,0:52:54.29,Default,,0,0,0,,And therefore, they put themselves out of business,
Dialogue: 0,0:52:54.29,0:52:55.83,Default,,0,0,0,,usually in 200 to 300 years.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:57.39,0:53:02.53,Default,,0,0,0,,So, the wisdom of the elders, their respect for experience,
Dialogue: 0,0:53:03.97,0:53:04.97,Default,,0,0,0,,legitimate.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:06.30,0:53:07.06,Default,,0,0,0,,What is authority?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:07.24,0:53:12.54,Default,,0,0,0,,So, true authority is integrity of essence.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:12.82,0:53:13.60,Default,,0,0,0,,That's true authority.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:14.44,0:53:20.16,Default,,0,0,0,,You know how to do a thing because you've successfully done it.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:20.38,0:53:22.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Now you've got the true authority
Dialogue: 0,0:53:22.46,0:53:25.98,Default,,0,0,0,,to differentiate it from false authority.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:26.16,0:53:28.50,Default,,0,0,0,,So, rebelling against false authority is one thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:29.59,0:53:32.39,Default,,0,0,0,,To rebel against true authority shows a certain ignorance.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:32.77,0:53:36.29,Default,,0,0,0,,So, there's a great value to the wisdom of the elders.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:36.33,0:53:39.61,Default,,0,0,0,,And, if it wasn't for the council of the elders,
Dialogue: 0,0:53:39.89,0:53:43.64,Default,,0,0,0,,most of many societies would not have existed.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:44.82,0:53:48.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Because the elder, to me, an elder is one who's had it with the world
Dialogue: 0,0:53:48.26,0:53:50.90,Default,,0,0,0,,and really doesn't need or want anything more from it.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:52.28,0:53:53.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Who's that big financier?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:53.60,0:53:53.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Buffett.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:54.06,0:53:55.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Buffett, people like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:55.84,0:53:56.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, he's made trillions.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:57.00,0:53:57.96,Default,,0,0,0,,He don't need any more money.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:58.40,0:54:01.64,Default,,0,0,0,,So, what he shares, he shares out of the integrity and value
Dialogue: 0,0:54:01.64,0:54:02.84,Default,,0,0,0,,of his own inner experience.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:02.96,0:54:03.66,Default,,0,0,0,,This is what I did.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:03.72,0:54:04.36,Default,,0,0,0,,This is what I learned.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:04.36,0:54:05.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I share it with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:05.20,0:54:09.38,Default,,0,0,0,,So, Warren Buffett is an authority.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:09.38,0:54:13.10,Default,,0,0,0,,So, we don't, you know, have the Dixie Chicks parading, you know,
Dialogue: 0,0:54:13.10,0:54:14.98,Default,,0,0,0,,screwing Warren Buffett.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:14.98,0:54:24.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I got a kick out of that time cover,
Dialogue: 0,0:54:24.14,0:54:25.86,Default,,0,0,0,,especially the girl on the far right.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:25.86,0:54:27.06,Default,,0,0,0,,You can just calibrate her.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:27.06,0:54:29.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Just by looking at her face, you know what she calibrates.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:29.50,0:54:31.66,Default,,0,0,0,,If that ain't 170 or 180, I never saw it.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:31.66,0:54:37.00,Default,,0,0,0,,It's like, in your face, in your face.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:40.22,0:54:42.41,Default,,0,0,0,,It's funny.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:42.41,0:54:44.77,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't see people doing that with Warren Buffett, do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:44.77,0:54:47.18,Default,,0,0,0,,We have a little surprise.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:47.18,0:54:47.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh-huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:47.92,0:54:49.42,Default,,0,0,0,,What, is it time for a break?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:49.42,0:54:50.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Almost.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:50.04,0:54:51.62,Default,,0,0,0,,But we have a little surprise for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:51.62,0:54:52.40,Default,,0,0,0,,A little one?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:52.40,0:54:53.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:53.14,0:55:00.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, where's my surprise?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:01.72,0:55:13.76,Default,,0,0,0,,We don't have anybody say, we disrespect Warren Buffett.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:13.76,0:55:18.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't that funny to think of it?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:18.26,0:55:19.70,Default,,0,0,0,,We disrespect Warren Buffett.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:19.70,0:55:24.46,Default,,0,0,0,,It came for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:24.46,0:55:25.66,Default,,0,0,0,,It's good.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:25.66,0:55:26.66,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a good description.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:26.66,0:55:27.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:27.66,0:55:28.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't that fantastic?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:28.66,0:55:29.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:29.66,0:55:31.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow, wow.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:31.71,0:55:32.71,Default,,0,0,0,,That's all I can say about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:32.71,0:55:39.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:39.18,0:55:40.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, this is the big 8-0 coming up.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:40.18,0:55:45.22,Default,,0,0,0,,You know what I'm saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:45.22,0:55:47.27,Default,,0,0,0,,So, I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:47.27,0:55:54.58,Default,,0,0,0,,When do you become an elder?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:54.58,0:55:55.58,Default,,0,0,0,,When you, I think 8-0 makes it.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:55.58,0:56:02.14,Default,,0,0,0,,To be alive and kicking at 8-0 is still okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:02.14,0:56:03.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you get to read what it say?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:03.14,0:56:04.85,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:04.85,0:56:05.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Before we cut it?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:05.85,0:56:06.85,Default,,0,0,0,,We want you to read it.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:06.85,0:56:08.78,Default,,0,0,0,,We want you to read it.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:08.78,0:56:09.78,Default,,0,0,0,,We want you to read it.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:09.78,0:56:10.78,Default,,0,0,0,,We want you to read it.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:10.78,0:56:11.78,Default,,0,0,0,,We want you to read it.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:11.78,0:56:12.78,Default,,0,0,0,,We want you to read it.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:12.78,0:56:13.81,Default,,0,0,0,,We want you to read it.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:13.81,0:56:14.81,Default,,0,0,0,,We want you to read it.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:14.81,0:56:17.92,Default,,0,0,0,,To be alive and kicking at 8-0 is still okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:17.92,0:56:18.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you get to read what it say?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:18.92,0:56:19.92,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:19.92,0:56:20.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Before we cut it?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:20.92,0:56:21.92,Default,,0,0,0,,We want you to see.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:21.92,0:56:22.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Gloria in Excelsior's deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:22.92,0:56:23.92,Default,,0,0,0,,There you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:23.92,0:56:24.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, what a perfect birthday I've had.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:24.98,0:56:25.98,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:25.98,0:56:26.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you all.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:26.98,0:56:27.98,Default,,0,0,0,,You can relax.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:27.98,0:56:28.98,Default,,0,0,0,,And I got my Father's Day present ready too.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:28.98,0:56:29.98,Default,,0,0,0,,A new cat.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:29.98,0:56:36.04,Default,,0,0,0,,A new cat.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:36.04,0:56:37.04,Default,,0,0,0,,A new cat.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:37.04,0:56:38.04,Default,,0,0,0,,A new cat.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:38.04,0:56:39.04,Default,,0,0,0,,A new cat.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:39.04,0:56:40.04,Default,,0,0,0,,A new cat.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:40.04,0:56:41.04,Default,,0,0,0,,A new cat.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:41.04,0:56:42.04,Default,,0,0,0,,A new cat.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:42.04,0:56:43.04,Default,,0,0,0,,A new cat.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:43.04,0:56:44.04,Default,,0,0,0,,A new cat.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:44.04,0:56:45.04,Default,,0,0,0,,A new cat.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:45.04,0:56:46.55,Default,,0,0,0,,A new cat.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:46.55,0:56:47.55,Default,,0,0,0,,A new cat.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:47.55,0:56:48.55,Default,,0,0,0,,A new cat.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:48.55,0:56:49.55,Default,,0,0,0,,A new cat.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:49.55,0:56:51.35,Default,,0,0,0,,A new cat.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:51.35,0:56:52.35,Default,,0,0,0,,A new cat.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:52.35,0:56:53.35,Default,,0,0,0,,A new cat.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:53.35,0:56:54.35,Default,,0,0,0,,A new cat.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:54.35,0:56:55.35,Default,,0,0,0,,A new cat.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:55.35,0:56:56.35,Default,,0,0,0,,A new cat.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:56.35,0:56:57.35,Default,,0,0,0,,A new cat.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:57.35,0:56:58.35,Default,,0,0,0,,A new cat.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:58.35,0:56:59.35,Default,,0,0,0,,A new cat.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:59.35,0:57:00.35,Default,,0,0,0,,A new cat.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:00.35,0:57:01.61,Default,,0,0,0,,A new cat.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:01.61,0:57:02.61,Default,,0,0,0,,A new cat.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:02.61,0:57:03.61,Default,,0,0,0,,A new cat.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:03.61,0:57:04.61,Default,,0,0,0,,A new cat.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:04.61,0:57:05.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:05.61,0:57:06.61,Default,,0,0,0,,A new cat.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:06.61,0:57:09.82,Default,,0,0,0,,A new cat.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:09.82,0:57:10.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:10.82,0:57:11.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Plus we have two little kittens to begin with.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:11.82,0:57:12.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Now we've got, so now we're going to have three new cats anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:12.82,0:57:13.82,Default,,0,0,0,,It's why it's interesting to watch them interact, you see.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:13.82,0:57:14.82,Default,,0,0,0,,We brought in two male-castrated.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:14.82,0:57:15.82,Default,,0,0,0,,The quickest way to heaven, fellas, is to get castrated.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:15.82,0:57:16.82,Default,,0,0,0,,It'll save you all kinds of trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:16.82,0:57:21.34,Default,,0,0,0,,All kinds of trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:21.34,0:57:22.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:22.34,0:57:24.99,Default,,0,0,0,,We brought in the new cat.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:24.99,0:57:26.82,Default,,0,0,0,,We were a little apprehensive.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:26.82,0:57:29.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:29.22,0:57:30.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:30.22,0:57:31.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I hope you guys enjoyed it.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:31.22,0:57:32.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Are they going to get along?
Dialogue: 0,0:57:32.42,0:57:34.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I was projecting my protectionism
Dialogue: 0,0:57:34.18,0:57:37.02,Default,,0,0,0,,to not hurt the feelings of the older cat.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:37.14,0:57:37.96,Default,,0,0,0,,There's new ones here.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:39.12,0:57:41.72,Default,,0,0,0,,And then I just surrendered the whole thing to God.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:42.04,0:57:43.14,Default,,0,0,0,,And they get along beautifully.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:43.24,0:57:44.08,Default,,0,0,0,,They love each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:45.82,0:57:47.84,Default,,0,0,0,,And they're very respectful of elders.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:48.46,0:57:50.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, the young cat, you know,
Dialogue: 0,0:57:50.82,0:57:52.28,Default,,0,0,0,,could beat up the old cat easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:52.60,0:57:56.04,Default,,0,0,0,,But what happens is the young cat stands back
Dialogue: 0,0:57:56.04,0:57:57.44,Default,,0,0,0,,and lets the elder have his dinner.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:58.22,0:57:59.32,Default,,0,0,0,,He just lays there patiently.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:59.32,0:58:01.30,Default,,0,0,0,,When the elder's done, he walks over
Dialogue: 0,0:58:01.30,0:58:01.98,Default,,0,0,0,,and has his.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:02.18,0:58:03.24,Default,,0,0,0,,So perfect harmony.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:03.86,0:58:04.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't that neat?
Dialogue: 0,0:58:04.60,0:58:05.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Perfect harmony.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:05.84,0:58:07.56,Default,,0,0,0,,And they get along wonderfully.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:08.58,0:58:09.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course, they don't know
Dialogue: 0,0:58:09.46,0:58:10.88,Default,,0,0,0,,there's two little kittens waiting
Dialogue: 0,0:58:10.88,0:58:12.06,Default,,0,0,0,,to come in and join the crowd.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:13.26,0:58:14.94,Default,,0,0,0,,You see how happy they are then.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:18.10,0:58:20.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, Susan and I were joking about
Dialogue: 0,0:58:20.04,0:58:21.82,Default,,0,0,0,,the most dangerous thing on the planet
Dialogue: 0,0:58:21.82,0:58:22.72,Default,,0,0,0,,is testosterone.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:23.66,0:58:26.44,Default,,0,0,0,,The most dangerous substance on the planet
Dialogue: 0,0:58:26.44,0:58:27.26,Default,,0,0,0,,is testosterone.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:27.60,0:58:30.74,Default,,0,0,0,,It's killed more people than all anything in history.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:31.82,0:58:32.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Testosterone.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:33.41,0:58:35.45,Default,,0,0,0,,The mad, crazed hordes.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:36.26,0:58:37.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Savaging, chopping off people,
Dialogue: 0,0:58:38.12,0:58:39.18,Default,,0,0,0,,butchering people.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:40.41,0:58:43.19,Default,,0,0,0,,So, you know, universal castration
Dialogue: 0,0:58:43.19,0:58:45.41,Default,,0,0,0,,might bring us all to heaven earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:45.65,0:58:46.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:54.38,0:58:56.38,Default,,0,0,0,,You're going to be very popular today.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:59.40,0:59:03.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway, those things are all part of our karmic inheritance.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:04.66,0:59:07.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Because of the evolutionary nature of human nature,
Dialogue: 0,0:59:07.72,0:59:08.70,Default,,0,0,0,,you know, we evolved.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:09.12,0:59:10.30,Default,,0,0,0,,As you can see, our consciousness
Dialogue: 0,0:59:10.68,0:59:13.48,Default,,0,0,0,,evolved from the protozoa, the amoeba,
Dialogue: 0,0:59:13.66,0:59:15.34,Default,,0,0,0,,on up through all of evolution.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:16.14,0:59:18.66,Default,,0,0,0,,And you see, you know, that evolution and creation
Dialogue: 0,0:59:18.66,0:59:20.02,Default,,0,0,0,,are one and the same thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:20.10,0:59:21.32,Default,,0,0,0,,That is so simple to see.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:22.69,0:59:25.31,Default,,0,0,0,,The intelligent design argument, of course,
Dialogue: 0,0:59:25.41,0:59:27.57,Default,,0,0,0,,is political posturing.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:28.55,0:59:31.01,Default,,0,0,0,,And one reason they don't like it
Dialogue: 0,0:59:31.01,0:59:32.67,Default,,0,0,0,,is the idea of the slippery slope.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:33.79,0:59:35.85,Default,,0,0,0,,The slippery slope argument, of course,
Dialogue: 0,0:59:35.85,0:59:37.15,Default,,0,0,0,,is fallacious.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:37.85,0:59:39.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Because it's the hypothetical.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:39.55,0:59:40.83,Default,,0,0,0,,And the hypothetical is not,
Dialogue: 0,0:59:40.87,0:59:42.87,Default,,0,0,0,,you know, not real, you know, not real.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:44.40,0:59:46.78,Default,,0,0,0,,But anyway, the creation and evolution
Dialogue: 0,0:59:46.78,0:59:47.92,Default,,0,0,0,,are one and the same thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:47.92,0:59:49.24,Default,,0,0,0,,It's so easy to see.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:49.72,0:59:52.36,Default,,0,0,0,,In fact, we calibrate it to grasp
Dialogue: 0,0:59:52.36,0:59:54.84,Default,,0,0,0,,that evolution and creation are one and the same thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:55.91,0:59:58.75,Default,,0,0,0,,That evolution is the way creation appears.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:58.75,1:00:02.11,Default,,0,0,0,,In other words, creation is progressive.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:02.96,1:00:04.98,Default,,0,0,0,,And it was created to be that way.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:05.32,1:00:07.98,Default,,0,0,0,,You only have to calibrate it at 375.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:07.98,1:00:11.94,Default,,0,0,0,,From 375 on is the level of consciousness required.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:12.78,1:00:14.70,Default,,0,0,0,,To sort of enqueue it and be able to see,
Dialogue: 0,1:00:14.88,1:00:16.60,Default,,0,0,0,,oh yes, evolution and creation.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:17.46,1:00:20.56,Default,,0,0,0,,The way creation appears is evolutionary, right?
Dialogue: 0,1:00:20.72,1:00:21.34,Default,,0,0,0,,It's simple.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:22.04,1:00:23.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Simple, very simple to see.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:23.50,1:00:24.74,Default,,0,0,0,,It only takes 375.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:25.34,1:00:29.80,Default,,0,0,0,,So, because America is at 420-something or other,
Dialogue: 0,1:00:30.92,1:00:32.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, it's most of America, you know,
Dialogue: 0,1:00:32.38,1:00:38.09,Default,,0,0,0,,the capacity to understand the reality is there.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:38.85,1:00:40.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Then comes the willingness.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:41.39,1:00:42.01,Default,,0,0,0,,And then, of course,
Dialogue: 0,1:00:42.47,1:00:44.37,Default,,0,0,0,,the difficulty with today's world
Dialogue: 0,1:00:44.37,1:00:45.91,Default,,0,0,0,,is nobody knows who to trust.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:46.59,1:00:48.89,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the subject of the chapters
Dialogue: 0,1:00:48.89,1:00:50.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm working on right now for a new book.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:51.86,1:00:54.02,Default,,0,0,0,,How can you trust anymore?
Dialogue: 0,1:00:54.50,1:00:55.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Who can you trust?
Dialogue: 0,1:00:55.54,1:00:57.34,Default,,0,0,0,,In fact, isn't trust untrustable?
Dialogue: 0,1:00:58.78,1:01:01.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't it stupid to trust anything or anyone?
Dialogue: 0,1:01:02.56,1:01:06.66,Default,,0,0,0,,So, you see a protective skepticism in society.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:09.23,1:01:12.07,Default,,0,0,0,,And in spiritual history, and currently, you can see
Dialogue: 0,1:01:12.07,1:01:12.91,Default,,0,0,0,,that unless you trust, you can't trust.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:12.91,1:01:13.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Unless you trust, you can't trust.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:13.15,1:01:13.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Unless you trust, you can't trust.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:13.25,1:01:13.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Unless you trust, you can't trust.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:13.27,1:01:14.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Unless truth is corroborated,
Dialogue: 0,1:01:14.81,1:01:16.41,Default,,0,0,0,,you are taking a certain risk.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:17.33,1:01:20.88,Default,,0,0,0,,And if you have faith in a good teacher
Dialogue: 0,1:01:20.88,1:01:23.34,Default,,0,0,0,,and the teacher fulfills all the requirements,
Dialogue: 0,1:01:24.08,1:01:28.18,Default,,0,0,0,,then a good teacher will direct you to a source of truth
Dialogue: 0,1:01:28.18,1:01:29.30,Default,,0,0,0,,that's independent of him.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:29.42,1:01:30.02,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't need him.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:31.28,1:01:32.96,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, once he's given you the word,
Dialogue: 0,1:01:33.06,1:01:33.76,Default,,0,0,0,,what do you need him for?
Dialogue: 0,1:01:34.62,1:01:35.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Get rid of it.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:36.24,1:01:37.18,Default,,0,0,0,,You're on your own.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:38.24,1:01:40.20,Default,,0,0,0,,So, the teacher then, you know,
Dialogue: 0,1:01:40.22,1:01:41.52,Default,,0,0,0,,supports your inspiration,
Dialogue: 0,1:01:42.44,1:01:43.66,Default,,0,0,0,,tries to share, you know,
Dialogue: 0,1:01:43.66,1:01:44.78,Default,,0,0,0,,your personal experience,
Dialogue: 0,1:01:45.60,1:01:49.82,Default,,0,0,0,,tries to show the way to the verifiable truth,
Dialogue: 0,1:01:50.66,1:01:51.92,Default,,0,0,0,,and then you're on your own.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:52.16,1:01:54.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Because the teacher wants nothing from you,
Dialogue: 0,1:01:55.10,1:01:55.92,Default,,0,0,0,,except a cake.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:58.18,1:01:59.74,Default,,0,0,0,,He did want a blue cake.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:59.84,1:02:00.96,Default,,0,0,0,,He did want a blue cake.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:02.16,1:02:03.24,Default,,0,0,0,,He did want a blue cake.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:04.26,1:02:05.74,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, we're going to take a break,
Dialogue: 0,1:02:06.02,1:02:08.52,Default,,0,0,0,,and then we'll reconvene in, what, 15 minutes?
Dialogue: 0,1:02:11.65,1:02:12.57,Default,,0,0,0,,We are right now?
Dialogue: 0,1:02:12.83,1:02:16.09,Default,,0,0,0,,The cake will be in the cafeteria.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:16.57,1:02:17.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:17.15,1:02:17.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:17.73,1:02:19.07,Default,,0,0,0,,We can all have a piece of cake.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:19.91,1:02:21.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Life's a piece of cake, ain't it?
Dialogue: 0,1:02:21.73,1:02:39.22,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, I share with you what I know,
Dialogue: 0,1:02:39.56,1:02:43.02,Default,,0,0,0,,and it's sort of an intuitive, you just know it.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:43.22,1:02:45.78,Default,,0,0,0,,And this morning we got our wrong answers,
Dialogue: 0,1:02:45.90,1:02:47.78,Default,,0,0,0,,which gave us a wonderful chance to,
Dialogue: 0,1:02:47.92,1:02:50.58,Default,,0,0,0,,we try to show a little bit about kinesiology every time.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:51.58,1:02:53.80,Default,,0,0,0,,And this morning we demonstrated a thing we,
Dialogue: 0,1:02:54.66,1:02:57.70,Default,,0,0,0,,remember I said the Hindu tradition is
Dialogue: 0,1:02:57.70,1:02:59.60,Default,,0,0,0,,that you can come back if you've got bad karma.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:00.78,1:03:02.22,Default,,0,0,0,,That was a lower animal.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:02.98,1:03:03.90,Default,,0,0,0,,And I've always said,
Dialogue: 0,1:03:03.96,1:03:04.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I've always gotten no.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:04.72,1:03:05.74,Default,,0,0,0,,This morning we got a yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:07.20,1:03:09.40,Default,,0,0,0,,So as I said, we'll have to research that out.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:10.32,1:03:15.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Which brings up, if you mill around with a lot of people
Dialogue: 0,1:03:15.53,1:03:17.35,Default,,0,0,0,,or expose yourself to music, et cetera,
Dialogue: 0,1:03:18.07,1:03:20.59,Default,,0,0,0,,you can sort of go out,
Dialogue: 0,1:03:20.71,1:03:22.77,Default,,0,0,0,,your energies go out without you realizing it.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:23.71,1:03:24.55,Default,,0,0,0,,It happened to Susan.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:24.69,1:03:26.95,Default,,0,0,0,,She said, you know, I felt something go out,
Dialogue: 0,1:03:27.01,1:03:30.57,Default,,0,0,0,,and I just cleared it in myself with a diamond thump.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:31.50,1:03:33.62,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, you hold somebody you love in mind,
Dialogue: 0,1:03:33.62,1:03:36.09,Default,,0,0,0,,thump, thump, smile.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:37.29,1:03:39.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Ha, ha, ha, ha, ha, ha, ha.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:39.75,1:03:41.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, she did that.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:41.99,1:03:43.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, let's ask the question again.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:46.28,1:03:49.26,Default,,0,0,0,,The ancient Hindu belief is that with bad karma
Dialogue: 0,1:03:49.26,1:03:50.78,Default,,0,0,0,,you can come back as a lesser creature.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:51.46,1:03:52.58,Default,,0,0,0,,That is true, it is.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:53.90,1:03:56.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, that's always the answer we've gotten.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:57.04,1:04:00.64,Default,,0,0,0,,So if anything is in doubt, just do the thiamic thump.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:01.77,1:04:03.79,Default,,0,0,0,,You hold in mind somebody you love,
Dialogue: 0,1:04:04.90,1:04:06.76,Default,,0,0,0,,you thump over the thiamin's cornea and say,
Dialogue: 0,1:04:06.76,1:04:07.50,Default,,0,0,0,,ha, ha, ha.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:08.06,1:04:09.42,Default,,0,0,0,,And that corrects the imbalance.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:09.44,1:04:11.02,Default,,0,0,0,,And that corrects the imbalance in the acupuncture system.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:12.05,1:04:14.53,Default,,0,0,0,,So I don't like to bring out, you know,
Dialogue: 0,1:04:14.55,1:04:15.57,Default,,0,0,0,,because it makes you paranoid,
Dialogue: 0,1:04:15.77,1:04:17.43,Default,,0,0,0,,but actually anybody can blow you out
Dialogue: 0,1:04:17.43,1:04:19.07,Default,,0,0,0,,if they have a very negative energy.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:19.97,1:04:22.45,Default,,0,0,0,,And half of America gets blown out every night
Dialogue: 0,1:04:22.45,1:04:24.81,Default,,0,0,0,,watching the news because people who come up
Dialogue: 0,1:04:24.81,1:04:28.05,Default,,0,0,0,,and calibrate about 160 are very,
Dialogue: 0,1:04:28.83,1:04:30.85,Default,,0,0,0,,it's the energy with which they put it forth,
Dialogue: 0,1:04:31.01,1:04:32.29,Default,,0,0,0,,the fervor, you know what I mean?
Dialogue: 0,1:04:33.47,1:04:36.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Like if evil is destroyed, they're going to go up in flames
Dialogue: 0,1:04:36.03,1:04:38.43,Default,,0,0,0,,so they make sure that evil is going to stay here.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:38.43,1:04:39.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Ha, ha, ha, ha.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:39.61,1:04:40.31,Default,,0,0,0,,And I don't like to bring out, you know,
Dialogue: 0,1:04:40.31,1:04:41.43,Default,,0,0,0,,after you watch them.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:42.76,1:04:45.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder what, let's, I'm going to ask this.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:46.39,1:04:47.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Can we ask the percentage of people
Dialogue: 0,1:04:47.87,1:04:49.95,Default,,0,0,0,,that get blown out watching the evening news
Dialogue: 0,1:04:49.95,1:04:52.51,Default,,0,0,0,,in the naive populace?
Dialogue: 0,1:04:53.07,1:04:56.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Probably over 30%, 50%.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:56.07,1:04:58.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Probably over 40%.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:58.13,1:05:00.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Probably 40% their whole energy field
Dialogue: 0,1:05:00.69,1:05:02.27,Default,,0,0,0,,is reversed by the evening news.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:04.57,1:05:06.81,Default,,0,0,0,,That's one of the reasons it's spiritual tradition.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:06.91,1:05:08.55,Default,,0,0,0,,One spiritual tradition, of course,
Dialogue: 0,1:05:09.50,1:05:11.00,Default,,0,0,0,,is that of the renunciate,
Dialogue: 0,1:05:11.00,1:05:11.96,Default,,0,0,0,,which renounces the world,
Dialogue: 0,1:05:11.96,1:05:14.26,Default,,0,0,0,,does not expose himself to that negativity
Dialogue: 0,1:05:14.26,1:05:17.16,Default,,0,0,0,,because he had no means to defend himself
Dialogue: 0,1:05:17.16,1:05:20.26,Default,,0,0,0,,nor, you know, could he do kinesiology
Dialogue: 0,1:05:20.26,1:05:22.74,Default,,0,0,0,,and find out that, hey, I just got blown out by something
Dialogue: 0,1:05:22.74,1:05:24.66,Default,,0,0,0,,and correct it, you know?
Dialogue: 0,1:05:26.26,1:05:28.18,Default,,0,0,0,,So that was sort of interesting, wasn't it?
Dialogue: 0,1:05:28.18,1:05:29.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm glad it happened.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:29.72,1:05:31.76,Default,,0,0,0,,And she intuited right away,
Dialogue: 0,1:05:31.82,1:05:33.28,Default,,0,0,0,,she said something must have gotten blown out
Dialogue: 0,1:05:33.28,1:05:35.27,Default,,0,0,0,,and she corrected it.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:35.43,1:05:39.32,Default,,0,0,0,,So that was a very interesting teaching example.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:40.46,1:05:42.86,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, this morning we did what we wanted to do.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:42.86,1:05:45.20,Default,,0,0,0,,We did what we wanted to do for the new information.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:45.20,1:05:47.60,Default,,0,0,0,,And so I want to go back, honey,
Dialogue: 0,1:05:47.60,1:05:51.04,Default,,0,0,0,,all right, we'll go back to the way we usually present it.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:51.04,1:05:54.30,Default,,0,0,0,,We usually present it more academically.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:56.04,1:05:58.26,Default,,0,0,0,,But every time we go back over the same material,
Dialogue: 0,1:05:58.26,1:06:01.52,Default,,0,0,0,,we learn something new, re-exposure.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:02.70,1:06:05.54,Default,,0,0,0,,And of course, you learn, as Dr. Kalmbach says,
Dialogue: 0,1:06:05.54,1:06:07.64,Default,,0,0,0,,repetition is the world's best teacher.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:09.84,1:06:11.28,Default,,0,0,0,,You struggle to understand it,
Dialogue: 0,1:06:11.28,1:06:12.86,Default,,0,0,0,,but after you've heard it about six times,
Dialogue: 0,1:06:12.86,1:06:16.82,Default,,0,0,0,,it's like, yeah, I mean, you've like incorporated it, you see?
Dialogue: 0,1:06:17.44,1:06:20.16,Default,,0,0,0,,So that's the Kalmbach principle that we...
Dialogue: 0,1:06:22.83,1:06:27.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Unity Church, announce the Unity Church.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:27.12,1:06:29.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, you announced that, I don't remember.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:30.10,1:06:32.82,Default,,0,0,0,,She forgot to announce something, Unity Church.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:33.56,1:06:35.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, this coming Sunday, oh yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:42.17,1:06:42.95,Default,,0,0,0,,The sermon.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:43.45,1:06:45.53,Default,,0,0,0,,The sermon, I said sermon.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:45.71,1:06:47.45,Default,,0,0,0,,The sermon, what is it, 9 and 11?
Dialogue: 0,1:06:47.45,1:06:49.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I think it's 9 and 11.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:49.81,1:06:51.87,Default,,0,0,0,,You can go to the website and stuff like that.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:51.89,1:06:52.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:52.39,1:06:57.20,Default,,0,0,0,,And we'll be speaking at Unity Church this next weekend, the 25th.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:57.20,1:07:02.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know, it's a very small church.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:02.28,1:07:05.08,Default,,0,0,0,,You do have to make a reservation.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:05.08,1:07:11.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, well, it's a small church, and we might just blow their socks off, so.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:11.36,1:07:15.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm just warning you, it might be crowded.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:15.52,1:07:20.07,Default,,0,0,0,,The minister is Sandra Keep, a very sweet lady.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:20.07,1:07:24.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I spoke at Unity when I first came to Sedona.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:24.07,1:07:27.07,Default,,0,0,0,,They introduced the Course in Miracles, didn't they?
Dialogue: 0,1:07:27.07,1:07:29.97,Default,,0,0,0,,They didn't have it in Sedona, and you couldn't get it in the bookstore.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:29.97,1:07:34.03,Default,,0,0,0,,And we gave a lecture on the Course in Miracles.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:34.03,1:07:38.13,Default,,0,0,0,,And at the end of which, we had 100 members.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:38.13,1:07:42.13,Default,,0,0,0,,And the population of Sedona at that time was 3,000.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:42.13,1:07:51.13,Default,,0,0,0,,So, 100 members meditating, according to research done by, I forget what spiritual group it is,
Dialogue: 0,1:07:51.13,1:07:54.58,Default,,0,0,0,,will actually affect the crime rate in the town.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:54.58,1:07:55.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Over 5%.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:55.58,1:07:56.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Over 5%.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:56.58,1:08:01.58,Default,,0,0,0,,5% of the population meditates, etc.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:01.58,1:08:04.58,Default,,0,0,0,,The crime rate in the town actually decreases.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:04.58,1:08:10.90,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, the Maharishi's organization, I forget the name of it.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:10.90,1:08:15.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Whatever.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:15.65,1:08:19.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:19.98,1:08:29.79,Default,,0,0,0,,The other celebrity news of the week is, last week we were on Channel 3.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:29.79,1:08:32.89,Default,,0,0,0,,What's that nice lady's name?
Dialogue: 0,1:08:32.89,1:08:35.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Tanya Mock, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:36.59,1:08:37.59,Default,,0,0,0,,And Lee.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:37.59,1:08:39.59,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a wonderful program to be on.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:39.59,1:08:41.59,Default,,0,0,0,,And we ran a whole half hour.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:41.59,1:08:42.59,Default,,0,0,0,,We had such a good time.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:42.59,1:08:46.59,Default,,0,0,0,,And we talked about all these things that I thought would really blow the socks off people.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:46.59,1:08:47.59,Default,,0,0,0,,And they actually liked it.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:47.59,1:08:50.59,Default,,0,0,0,,And we did kinesiology right on the show and used her as the example.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:50.59,1:08:52.10,Default,,0,0,0,,It was fun.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:52.10,1:08:53.10,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:53.10,1:08:55.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Map of Consciousness.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:55.55,1:09:01.55,Default,,0,0,0,,We, of course, include this in all of our writings and we refer to it because the discovery
Dialogue: 0,1:09:01.55,1:09:03.55,Default,,0,0,0,,was sort of mind boggling.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:03.55,1:09:05.55,Default,,0,0,0,,And I've told you about the discovery.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:05.55,1:09:06.55,Default,,0,0,0,,That I had some people in the Course in Miracles.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:06.55,1:09:08.55,Default,,0,0,0,,And they did not respond.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:08.55,1:09:13.55,Default,,0,0,0,,They did not go weak to negative stimuli.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:13.55,1:09:15.55,Default,,0,0,0,,And that started the whole investigation.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:15.55,1:09:18.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I was going to give a lecture on kinesiology.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:18.62,1:09:23.84,Default,,0,0,0,,And I just grabbed these students of the Course in Miracles because we had an longitudinal
Dialogue: 0,1:09:23.84,1:09:28.84,Default,,0,0,0,,healing center there run by the Course in Miracles people for people with hopeless diseases.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:28.84,1:09:36.00,Default,,0,0,0,,And when they looked at, you know, everybody looks, if you're looking for fluorescent lights,
Dialogue: 0,1:09:36.00,1:09:37.00,Default,,0,0,0,,everybody goes weak.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:37.00,1:09:44.06,Default,,0,0,0,,And if you hold pesticides or the solar plexus or sweet and low, you go weak.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:44.06,1:09:46.06,Default,,0,0,0,,And these people didn't go weak with anything.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:46.06,1:09:48.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought, what?
Dialogue: 0,1:09:48.06,1:09:49.06,Default,,0,0,0,,They didn't go weak.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:49.06,1:09:53.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought they were sick or abnormal or something.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:53.06,1:09:56.06,Default,,0,0,0,,And then we began to research it with people who started the Course in Miracles.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:56.06,1:09:58.06,Default,,0,0,0,,We would test them in the beginning.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:58.06,1:10:01.16,Default,,0,0,0,,We tested them every couple of weeks.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:01.16,1:10:05.16,Default,,0,0,0,,And around about, less than 75, from there on up.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:05.16,1:10:12.26,Default,,0,0,0,,They no longer went weak because they realized, I'm only subject to what I hold in mind.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:12.26,1:10:16.26,Default,,0,0,0,,And therefore, they no longer went weak.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:16.26,1:10:18.26,Default,,0,0,0,,That was a really amazing discovery.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:18.26,1:10:25.26,Default,,0,0,0,,The shift in spiritual orientation can totally shift the response of your acupuncture system
Dialogue: 0,1:10:25.26,1:10:27.26,Default,,0,0,0,,and your whole physiology.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:27.26,1:10:32.26,Default,,0,0,0,,And of course, as we've learned since, also your brain physiology shifts from left brain
Dialogue: 0,1:10:32.26,1:10:33.26,Default,,0,0,0,,to right brain.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:33.26,1:10:35.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Your neurotransmitters change.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:35.26,1:10:38.93,Default,,0,0,0,,They change with spiritual intention.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:38.93,1:10:40.93,Default,,0,0,0,,And you put out endorphins.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:40.93,1:10:42.93,Default,,0,0,0,,And you perceive the world differently.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:42.93,1:10:47.93,Default,,0,0,0,,That gives us a certain compassion for people who see the world differently than we do.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:47.93,1:10:51.93,Default,,0,0,0,,It's because their brain physiology is such that that's the way they see it.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:51.93,1:10:54.93,Default,,0,0,0,,And they put out adrenaline.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:54.93,1:10:59.93,Default,,0,0,0,,And spiritually-oriented people see it with a compassionate understanding of the limitations
Dialogue: 0,1:10:59.93,1:11:02.12,Default,,0,0,0,,of human evolution.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:02.12,1:11:06.12,Default,,0,0,0,,And therefore, they see the world through prominently, right?
Dialogue: 0,1:11:06.12,1:11:11.12,Default,,0,0,0,,And they see it through the lens of their brain physiology and the influence of endorphins
Dialogue: 0,1:11:11.12,1:11:14.38,Default,,0,0,0,,rather than adrenaline or cortisone.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:14.38,1:11:17.38,Default,,0,0,0,,So that's going ahead of ourself.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:17.38,1:11:20.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway, we find this is extremely useful in many ways.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:20.38,1:11:25.38,Default,,0,0,0,,And of course, the book Truth Versus False, we demonstrate the many ways it can be used
Dialogue: 0,1:11:25.38,1:11:29.38,Default,,0,0,0,,from international politics to doing research.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:29.38,1:11:33.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm interested in it saving money in research.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:33.82,1:11:35.82,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, big foundations are about to put huge amounts of money in.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:35.82,1:11:37.89,Default,,0,0,0,,In various programs.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:37.89,1:11:39.89,Default,,0,0,0,,If they knew how to calibrate the programs,
Dialogue: 0,1:11:39.89,1:11:42.89,Default,,0,0,0,,they would know where their money would do the most good
Dialogue: 0,1:11:42.89,1:11:45.89,Default,,0,0,0,,instead of spending $100 million and finding it doesn't work.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:47.89,1:11:49.89,Default,,0,0,0,,$100 million on a project that doesn't work.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:49.89,1:11:50.89,Default,,0,0,0,,That's done all the time.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:50.89,1:11:54.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Look at the money that's been poured into Haiti.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:54.05,1:11:57.05,Default,,0,0,0,,And research shows the more money you pour into Haiti,
Dialogue: 0,1:11:57.05,1:12:00.05,Default,,0,0,0,,the worse the people become.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:00.05,1:12:04.05,Default,,0,0,0,,The more money you put in, the higher the poverty rate.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:04.05,1:12:06.05,Default,,0,0,0,,That you would know with kinesiology.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:06.05,1:12:08.05,Default,,0,0,0,,That you're doing something wrong.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:08.05,1:12:10.05,Default,,0,0,0,,You're making the people worse, not better.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:10.05,1:12:14.14,Default,,0,0,0,,So it's very useful for research.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:14.14,1:12:16.14,Default,,0,0,0,,So we're all very familiar with that.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:16.14,1:12:18.14,Default,,0,0,0,,And all the books refer to it in different ways.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:18.14,1:12:21.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Transcending Levels of Consciousness, of course,
Dialogue: 0,1:12:21.14,1:12:26.37,Default,,0,0,0,,shows us how to move from one level into another.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:26.37,1:12:29.78,Default,,0,0,0,,The willingness to let go of the payoff.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:29.78,1:12:33.78,Default,,0,0,0,,And if you feel like you're stuck anywhere, there's only one rule.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:33.78,1:12:35.78,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't have to worry about...
Dialogue: 0,1:12:36.78,1:12:39.82,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't have to worry about all these things here.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:39.82,1:12:41.82,Default,,0,0,0,,All these negative feelings.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:41.82,1:12:44.82,Default,,0,0,0,,All you have to figure out is one thing.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:44.82,1:12:48.26,Default,,0,0,0,,There's only one thing you only have to surrender.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:48.26,1:12:52.26,Default,,0,0,0,,The payoff you're getting from whatever positionality you're stuck in.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:52.26,1:12:54.26,Default,,0,0,0,,That's all you've got to let go of.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:54.26,1:12:57.67,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't have to let go of hating people.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:57.67,1:13:00.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Being afraid.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:00.34,1:13:03.34,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't have to let go of wanting to be a terrorist.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:04.34,1:13:06.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Blow up and bust loads of children.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:06.34,1:13:07.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I know that's tempting, but...
Dialogue: 0,1:13:07.34,1:13:10.21,Default,,0,0,0,,You have to forego the pleasure.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:10.21,1:13:16.22,Default,,0,0,0,,So it's the pleasure, gratification, and satisfaction
Dialogue: 0,1:13:16.22,1:13:18.22,Default,,0,0,0,,that you get out of that position.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:18.22,1:13:20.35,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what you're stuck on.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:20.35,1:13:21.35,Default,,0,0,0,,You understand?
Dialogue: 0,1:13:21.35,1:13:23.48,Default,,0,0,0,,You still hate your mother-in-law.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:23.48,1:13:25.48,Default,,0,0,0,,What you're stuck on is not your mother-in-law
Dialogue: 0,1:13:25.48,1:13:27.48,Default,,0,0,0,,and not your hatred.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:27.48,1:13:32.48,Default,,0,0,0,,What you're stuck on is that you get a satisfaction and a pleasure.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:32.48,1:13:37.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Like sort of a vengeful...
Dialogue: 0,1:13:37.79,1:13:40.79,Default,,0,0,0,,You only have to let go whatever payoff you're getting.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:40.79,1:13:42.79,Default,,0,0,0,,That payoff is an energy.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:42.79,1:13:45.79,Default,,0,0,0,,And once you identify it, you'll see it come up.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:45.79,1:13:48.21,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll see it come up.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:48.21,1:13:51.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Every negative thing that's holding you back from enlightenment
Dialogue: 0,1:13:51.21,1:13:55.21,Default,,0,0,0,,is due to the payoff that you're getting secretly from the ego.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:55.21,1:13:57.21,Default,,0,0,0,,You say, oh, I don't get any payoff.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:57.21,1:13:58.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yes, you do.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:58.21,1:14:00.21,Default,,0,0,0,,You get...
Dialogue: 0,1:14:00.21,1:14:02.21,Default,,0,0,0,,There's a lady that the far left is using right now.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:02.21,1:14:04.21,Default,,0,0,0,,They gallop her around.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:04.21,1:14:06.21,Default,,0,0,0,,And she gets arrested.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:06.21,1:14:08.21,Default,,0,0,0,,And when she got arrested,
Dialogue: 0,1:14:08.21,1:14:09.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll never forget that look.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:09.30,1:14:11.30,Default,,0,0,0,,She was like jubilant.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:11.30,1:14:13.30,Default,,0,0,0,,The police are taking her away.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:13.30,1:14:16.30,Default,,0,0,0,,And she's jubilant in a state of ecstasy.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:18.30,1:14:19.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Jubilant.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:19.30,1:14:20.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Jubilant.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:20.30,1:14:21.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:21.40,1:14:22.40,Default,,0,0,0,,There.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:22.40,1:14:25.40,Default,,0,0,0,,The satisfaction is gross and right on the surface.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:25.40,1:14:28.40,Default,,0,0,0,,With ourselves that are more sophisticated,
Dialogue: 0,1:14:28.40,1:14:31.40,Default,,0,0,0,,of course, we would repress the fact that we're getting off on it.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:34.90,1:14:37.90,Default,,0,0,0,,She got to be a celebrity, you know.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:37.90,1:14:39.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:39.99,1:14:40.99,Default,,0,0,0,,God bless her.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:40.99,1:14:42.99,Default,,0,0,0,,She was abused, I think.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:42.99,1:14:43.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:43.99,1:14:44.99,Default,,0,0,0,,So...
Dialogue: 0,1:14:44.99,1:14:46.50,Default,,0,0,0,,The payoff.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:46.50,1:14:50.50,Default,,0,0,0,,So just don't worry about sin and guilt and all that stuff.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:50.50,1:14:52.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Fear of hell and all that stuff.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:52.50,1:14:54.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Just look at what you're getting out of it.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:54.50,1:15:00.50,Default,,0,0,0,,And each one of these negative feelings is hooked in with others.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:00.50,1:15:02.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Each one is hooked in with others.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:02.86,1:15:05.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Not one of them ever exists alone.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:05.86,1:15:07.86,Default,,0,0,0,,You're angry because you're prideful,
Dialogue: 0,1:15:07.86,1:15:08.86,Default,,0,0,0,,because you're disappointed,
Dialogue: 0,1:15:08.86,1:15:10.86,Default,,0,0,0,,because you didn't acquire a gain.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:10.86,1:15:13.86,Default,,0,0,0,,You see, you've got five or six linked together.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:13.86,1:15:14.86,Default,,0,0,0,,So each...
Dialogue: 0,1:15:14.86,1:15:20.18,Default,,0,0,0,,So each brick that you pull out weakens the whole wall.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:20.18,1:15:23.18,Default,,0,0,0,,And eventually the whole ego collapses
Dialogue: 0,1:15:23.18,1:15:26.18,Default,,0,0,0,,because you see that there's only one thing
Dialogue: 0,1:15:26.18,1:15:28.18,Default,,0,0,0,,that you've been ever getting out of it all the time.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:28.18,1:15:31.18,Default,,0,0,0,,And that's the narcissistic core of the ego
Dialogue: 0,1:15:31.18,1:15:34.18,Default,,0,0,0,,loves to juice negativity because that's how it survives.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:34.18,1:15:36.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Without it, it can't survive.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:36.18,1:15:39.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Spiritual work is a tremendous threat
Dialogue: 0,1:15:39.18,1:15:42.59,Default,,0,0,0,,to the narcissistic core of the ego.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:42.59,1:15:43.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,1:15:43.59,1:15:44.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Because the narcissistic core of the ego,
Dialogue: 0,1:15:44.59,1:15:48.59,Default,,0,0,0,,considers itself to be divine.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:48.59,1:15:51.66,Default,,0,0,0,,It's God and it is the source of your life.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:51.66,1:15:55.98,Default,,0,0,0,,The ego has you convinced that without the ego you will die.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:55.98,1:15:58.98,Default,,0,0,0,,And then it is the core and source of your life.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:58.98,1:16:02.01,Default,,0,0,0,,And you don't really discover how powerful
Dialogue: 0,1:16:02.01,1:16:05.01,Default,,0,0,0,,and long-acting that has been, that delusion,
Dialogue: 0,1:16:05.01,1:16:08.01,Default,,0,0,0,,until you face what I call the final door
Dialogue: 0,1:16:08.01,1:16:11.01,Default,,0,0,0,,of infinite silence and infinite nothingness.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:11.01,1:16:14.01,Default,,0,0,0,,You've got nothing left to surrender to God except your life.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:14.01,1:16:16.01,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the only thing you've got left.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:16.01,1:16:18.01,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't have any programs.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:18.01,1:16:20.01,Default,,0,0,0,,There's nobody there.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:20.01,1:16:23.90,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no angel guides and all that stuff you read about.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:23.90,1:16:26.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Absolute alone.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:26.96,1:16:29.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Absolute silence.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:29.57,1:16:33.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing else to lay down except your life.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:33.82,1:16:37.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Then the terror comes up.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:37.56,1:16:41.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Unto thee, O Lord, do I surrender my life.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:41.56,1:16:46.07,Default,,0,0,0,,And then up comes the terror.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:46.07,1:16:48.23,Default,,0,0,0,,And it is a terror.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:48.23,1:16:51.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not going to tell you that it's pleasant and cheerful.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:51.23,1:16:54.23,Default,,0,0,0,,It is an absolute terror that you are dying.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:54.23,1:16:57.71,Default,,0,0,0,,And it's because you never have died.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:57.71,1:17:00.71,Default,,0,0,0,,You've only gone out of body and come back again.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:00.71,1:17:03.71,Default,,0,0,0,,You've never faced the narcissistic core of the ego,
Dialogue: 0,1:17:03.71,1:17:06.22,Default,,0,0,0,,which is your final.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:06.22,1:17:09.50,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the final.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:09.50,1:17:11.50,Default,,0,0,0,,And then you die.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:11.50,1:17:13.50,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't have to be afraid of dying.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:13.50,1:17:16.50,Default,,0,0,0,,You do.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:16.50,1:17:19.98,Default,,0,0,0,,After that, you don't have any fear of dying
Dialogue: 0,1:17:19.98,1:17:24.82,Default,,0,0,0,,because you already did it.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:24.82,1:17:26.82,Default,,0,0,0,,And so what else is new?
Dialogue: 0,1:17:26.82,1:17:35.54,Default,,0,0,0,,So the technology of spiritual evolution then
Dialogue: 0,1:17:35.54,1:17:39.54,Default,,0,0,0,,is to see that there's only one thing going on that's your enemy.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:39.54,1:17:41.57,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the unconscious payoff,
Dialogue: 0,1:17:41.57,1:17:45.57,Default,,0,0,0,,the narcissistic core the ego gets constantly,
Dialogue: 0,1:17:45.57,1:17:49.08,Default,,0,0,0,,secretly juicing everything.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:49.08,1:17:53.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I wish I had that picture of that lady on TV
Dialogue: 0,1:17:53.17,1:17:55.17,Default,,0,0,0,,because I'll never forget when the police hauled her away.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:55.17,1:17:57.17,Default,,0,0,0,,The jubilation.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:57.17,1:17:59.17,Default,,0,0,0,,And I thought, there's the narcissistic core of the ego.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:59.17,1:18:05.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Just getting all the glamour, the TV, the headlines.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:05.33,1:18:10.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, she was in her glory.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:10.62,1:18:15.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Just a simple person who would not understand anything we're talking about.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:15.00,1:18:17.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, we'll go on then.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:17.61,1:18:19.61,Default,,0,0,0,,So we always just review that.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:19.61,1:18:25.44,Default,,0,0,0,,We constantly confirm spiritual reality.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:25.44,1:18:28.44,Default,,0,0,0,,What we do is we calibrate all these things.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:28.44,1:18:30.44,Default,,0,0,0,,You see, I'll calibrate all these things.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:30.44,1:18:34.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Because it's spiritual belief.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:34.91,1:18:36.94,Default,,0,0,0,,And that's what I'm writing about now.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:36.94,1:18:41.39,Default,,0,0,0,,What can modern man, how can he handle spiritual reality?
Dialogue: 0,1:18:41.39,1:18:47.49,Default,,0,0,0,,First of all, in a society in which there isn't any truth available without expertise.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:47.49,1:18:51.65,Default,,0,0,0,,And how can he corroborate the truth of what he's reading?
Dialogue: 0,1:18:51.65,1:18:54.65,Default,,0,0,0,,What out of a couple of pages of old-fashioned scripture,
Dialogue: 0,1:18:54.65,1:18:57.65,Default,,0,0,0,,you know, is actual fact and believable?
Dialogue: 0,1:18:57.65,1:18:59.65,Default,,0,0,0,,And how much is just cultural myth?
Dialogue: 0,1:18:59.65,1:19:01.78,Default,,0,0,0,,The Old Testament, of course.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:01.78,1:19:03.78,Default,,0,0,0,,All old things like that.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:03.78,1:19:05.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Are full of all kinds of cultural myths.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:05.78,1:19:07.78,Default,,0,0,0,,And that's the whole Scopes trial dilemma.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:07.78,1:19:13.78,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, do you really believe that Jonah got swallowed into the stomach of a whale for three days?
Dialogue: 0,1:19:13.78,1:19:16.78,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, give me a break.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:16.78,1:19:19.78,Default,,0,0,0,,You can see Darrow's exasperation.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:19.78,1:19:21.78,Default,,0,0,0,,You want me to buy that?
Dialogue: 0,1:19:21.78,1:19:23.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Three days in the stomach of a whale?
Dialogue: 0,1:19:23.78,1:19:25.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Give me a break.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:25.94,1:19:27.94,Default,,0,0,0,,So that's modern man's dilemma.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:27.94,1:19:29.94,Default,,0,0,0,,To differentiate what is myth,
Dialogue: 0,1:19:29.94,1:19:32.03,Default,,0,0,0,,what is cultural myth,
Dialogue: 0,1:19:32.03,1:19:33.03,Default,,0,0,0,,what is legend.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:33.03,1:19:38.45,Default,,0,0,0,,And so much of ancient religious tradition incorporates a great deal of myth.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:38.45,1:19:40.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, we'll move on.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:40.45,1:19:45.98,Default,,0,0,0,,This is, we see, the majority of the world's population,
Dialogue: 0,1:19:45.98,1:19:48.98,Default,,0,0,0,,close to 80%,
Dialogue: 0,1:19:48.98,1:19:51.98,Default,,0,0,0,,calibrates below the level of integrity.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:51.98,1:19:56.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Which makes the daily news quite comprehensible, does it not?
Dialogue: 0,1:19:56.02,1:19:59.02,Default,,0,0,0,,If 80% of the people can't tell truth from falsehood,
Dialogue: 0,1:19:59.02,1:20:02.02,Default,,0,0,0,,and, you know, the,
Dialogue: 0,1:20:02.02,1:20:05.11,Default,,0,0,0,,these leaders are messianic,
Dialogue: 0,1:20:05.11,1:20:09.11,Default,,0,0,0,,narcissistic, messianic megalomania,
Dialogue: 0,1:20:09.11,1:20:11.27,Default,,0,0,0,,the world doesn't even know about that.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:11.27,1:20:13.30,Default,,0,0,0,,How do they know?
Dialogue: 0,1:20:13.30,1:20:16.82,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the same syndrome over and over.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:16.82,1:20:19.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Hitler, Stalin,
Dialogue: 0,1:20:19.39,1:20:23.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Pol Pot or Pot Paul, I never forget if he's a pot of Paul or a pole of pot.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:23.39,1:20:24.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Whatever it is.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:24.39,1:20:26.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Chairman Mayo.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:26.39,1:20:28.39,Default,,0,0,0,,They all calibrate the same.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:28.39,1:20:30.39,Default,,0,0,0,,They all have identical characteristics.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:30.39,1:20:32.39,Default,,0,0,0,,And mankind over and over gets slaughtered by them.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:32.39,1:20:35.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Not slaughtered, I mean 100 million.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:35.39,1:20:37.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Wouldn't that sort of wake you up a little bit?
Dialogue: 0,1:20:37.39,1:20:40.39,Default,,0,0,0,,100 million, wouldn't that be a wake-up call?
Dialogue: 0,1:20:40.39,1:20:42.39,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the cause of this?
Dialogue: 0,1:20:42.39,1:20:43.39,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the trigger?
Dialogue: 0,1:20:43.39,1:20:45.65,Default,,0,0,0,,100 million people by Stalin.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:45.65,1:20:48.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Another 100 million in World War II by Hitler.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:48.65,1:20:51.87,Default,,0,0,0,,The massacres of the Japanese in Manchuria.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:51.87,1:20:53.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Over and over and over again.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:53.87,1:20:57.87,Default,,0,0,0,,The Goths and the Slavs and the Genghis Khan.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:57.87,1:21:02.70,Default,,0,0,0,,All the mad czars of Russia.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:02.70,1:21:05.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Exterminating people by the hundreds of millions.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:05.70,1:21:08.70,Default,,0,0,0,,And the person who does it is identical.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:08.70,1:21:11.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Just has a different name, different era.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:11.70,1:21:13.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Calibrates the same.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:13.93,1:21:16.93,Default,,0,0,0,,And of course in truth versus falsehood we put a couple of pages.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:16.93,1:21:22.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Because mankind doesn't seem to be able to recognize the pathology involved.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:22.02,1:21:24.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, so we move on.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:24.02,1:21:29.02,Default,,0,0,0,,And of course this percentage of the population would not be able to see it.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:29.02,1:21:31.02,Default,,0,0,0,,This percentage of the population.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:31.02,1:21:32.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Because it lacks integrity.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:32.02,1:21:36.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Can't see non-integrity out there.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:36.02,1:21:37.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:37.02,1:21:38.02,Default,,0,0,0,,So the innocence.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:38.02,1:21:40.02,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the innocence of these people.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:40.02,1:21:41.02,Default,,0,0,0,,The ignorance.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:41.02,1:21:46.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Jesus Christ and the Buddha both say there's only one big problem and that is ignorance.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:46.02,1:21:48.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:48.25,1:21:51.25,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the rapidity of the evolution of consciousness.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:51.25,1:21:55.25,Default,,0,0,0,,According to dated history including up to the present.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:55.25,1:22:01.25,Default,,0,0,0,,And we see the evolution of consciousness until last week or so was going on pretty good.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:02.54,1:22:06.54,Default,,0,0,0,,West 207 now we see it's down to 206.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:06.54,1:22:08.57,Default,,0,0,0,,With a little research you can find out why.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:08.57,1:22:12.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Because you see for the collective to go down one point is a lot.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:12.57,1:22:16.70,Default,,0,0,0,,For one person to go down one point the world will not suffer.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:16.70,1:22:19.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Even one point is extremely important.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:19.70,1:22:22.70,Default,,0,0,0,,And why did the world go down one point?
Dialogue: 0,1:22:22.70,1:22:27.70,Default,,0,0,0,,You can research it with kinesiology.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:27.70,1:22:29.70,Default,,0,0,0,,What factors, what agreements.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:29.70,1:22:31.70,Default,,0,0,0,,What agreements.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:31.70,1:22:36.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Usually it's a collective agreement to a falsehood.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:36.18,1:22:38.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Collective support of a falsehood.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:38.18,1:22:40.62,Default,,0,0,0,,And then it comes down.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:40.62,1:22:41.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:41.62,1:22:42.66,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll move on.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:42.66,1:22:43.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Earth epics.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:43.66,1:22:45.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I think this is quite interesting.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:45.66,1:22:51.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Because it takes away the demonization of sin and error.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:51.85,1:22:55.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Because you see that consciousness is evolutionary.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:55.85,1:22:56.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Evolutionary.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:56.85,1:23:01.85,Default,,0,0,0,,If it's evolutionary, you know, what can I expect an octopus to know?
Dialogue: 0,1:23:02.85,1:23:04.85,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll move on.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:04.85,1:23:10.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I think it takes the guilt out of the ego.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:10.49,1:23:18.62,Default,,0,0,0,,If you see that the evolution was such that that's the way it evolved through creation.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:18.62,1:23:25.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Then you can stop feeling guilty about the ego and its obvious influence on our behaviors.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:25.62,1:23:31.71,Default,,0,0,0,,So we are part of an evolutionary species.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:31.71,1:23:36.03,Default,,0,0,0,,And this planet is the optimum spiritual school.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:36.03,1:23:40.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Optimum for spiritual advancement.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:40.19,1:23:42.19,Default,,0,0,0,,For karmic opportunity.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:42.19,1:23:47.19,Default,,0,0,0,,To undo negative karma and acquire positive karma.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:47.19,1:23:55.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Therefore, great catastrophes look horrendous on the surface.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:55.25,1:24:00.25,Default,,0,0,0,,At the same time, they undo tremendous amounts of negative karma.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:00.25,1:24:08.34,Default,,0,0,0,,And do mass amounts of negative karma.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:08.34,1:24:10.34,Default,,0,0,0,,So there's a certain benefit.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:10.34,1:24:12.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Hidden benefit to all that occurs.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:12.34,1:24:15.34,Default,,0,0,0,,It is not apparent to perception.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:15.34,1:24:17.34,Default,,0,0,0,,But if you use kinesiology.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:17.34,1:24:20.34,Default,,0,0,0,,And you say, did all the people in that benefit karmically?
Dialogue: 0,1:24:20.34,1:24:21.34,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll get yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:21.34,1:24:23.56,Default,,0,0,0,,They all paid off.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:23.56,1:24:25.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Huge debts all at once.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:25.56,1:24:27.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Plus they got to do it collectively.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:27.56,1:24:31.56,Default,,0,0,0,,So you're not all alone on the golf course when the lightning strikes you.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:34.56,1:24:36.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Octopus.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:36.62,1:24:38.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Here's octopus at 20.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:38.65,1:24:40.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to do the giant squid.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:40.65,1:24:43.22,Default,,0,0,0,,We never did the giant squid.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:43.22,1:24:44.22,Default,,0,0,0,,The giant squid.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:44.22,1:24:45.22,Default,,0,0,0,,We have permission.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:45.22,1:24:47.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Calibrates over 20.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:47.22,1:24:49.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Calibrates over 18.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:49.93,1:24:50.93,Default,,0,0,0,,19.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:50.93,1:24:52.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Giant squid is 18.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:52.93,1:24:55.46,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a ferocious beast.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:55.46,1:24:57.46,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't want to get involved with him.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:01.14,1:25:02.14,Default,,0,0,0,,The giant squid.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:02.14,1:25:05.14,Default,,0,0,0,,We try to calibrate everything we come across.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:05.14,1:25:06.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,1:25:06.14,1:25:10.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Because from the whole collective you begin to be able to intuit a thing.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:10.36,1:25:12.36,Default,,0,0,0,,To the point where you can look at it.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:12.36,1:25:13.36,Default,,0,0,0,,And guess.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:13.36,1:25:14.36,Default,,0,0,0,,You know.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:14.36,1:25:15.36,Default,,0,0,0,,That's about 180.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:15.36,1:25:16.36,Default,,0,0,0,,You know.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:16.36,1:25:18.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Somebody comes on some talk show at night.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:18.58,1:25:19.58,Default,,0,0,0,,And you got.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:19.58,1:25:20.58,Default,,0,0,0,,If that guy's over 180.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:20.58,1:25:21.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll eat my shirt.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:21.58,1:25:22.58,Default,,0,0,0,,You know what I mean?
Dialogue: 0,1:25:23.58,1:25:24.58,Default,,0,0,0,,On the other hand.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:24.58,1:25:26.58,Default,,0,0,0,,You can see people that are very, very integrous.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:26.58,1:25:28.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Even though you may not agree with them.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:28.58,1:25:29.58,Default,,0,0,0,,You know.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:29.58,1:25:30.58,Default,,0,0,0,,You can see it's coming out of their faith.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:30.58,1:25:33.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Out of their concern for mankind.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:33.58,1:25:36.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Out of their inner honesty.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:36.58,1:25:38.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Doesn't mean they can't make a mistake.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:38.58,1:25:39.58,Default,,0,0,0,,They can.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:39.58,1:25:40.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:40.74,1:25:41.74,Default,,0,0,0,,So we'll move on.
