Dialogue: 0,1:25:44.74,1:25:47.74,Default,,0,0,0,,The cat's purr and the dog.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:47.74,1:25:53.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I think are two pets that are like gifts to our inner child from God.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:53.74,1:25:57.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry you folks are all alone mankind and the planet.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:57.78,1:26:03.78,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll send you a doggy and a kitty.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:03.78,1:26:05.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I know they increase longevity.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:05.78,1:26:07.78,Default,,0,0,0,,People live longer who have pets.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:07.78,1:26:09.78,Default,,0,0,0,,And their health is higher.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:09.78,1:26:11.32,Default,,0,0,0,,It is a positive health.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:11.32,1:26:12.32,Default,,0,0,0,,And longevity benefit.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:12.32,1:26:13.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:13.32,1:26:14.32,Default,,0,0,0,,The great books of the western world I refer to often.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:14.32,1:26:15.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Because it is sort of the benchmark of intellectual integrity.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:15.42,1:26:16.61,Default,,0,0,0,,And anything that calibrates less than this would lack intellectual integrity.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:16.61,1:26:17.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,1:26:17.70,1:26:18.70,Default,,0,0,0,,So like we said.
